).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20the%20sacrifice%20means%20that%20the%20Hargreeves%20and%20Lila%20have%20been%20erased%20from%20history.%20Although%20no%20one%20has%20any%20memory%20of%20them%20in%20this%20timeline%2C%20the%20finale%20pays%20homage%20by%20including%20an%20end-credits%20scene%20that%20shows%20eight%20marigolds%20rapidly%20blooming%20in%20a%20patch%20of%20soil%20near%20a%20tree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhere's%20what%20happened%20to%20every%20major%20character%20in%20the%20fourth%20and%20final%20season%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Umbrella%20Academy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20the%20timeline%20is%20reset%20at%20the%20end%20of%20season%20three%2C%20Luther%20takes%20a%20job%20as%20a%20stripper.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221382%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Emmy%20Raver-Lampman%20as%20Allison%2C%20Elliot%20Page%20as%20Viktor%2C%20and%20Tom%20Hopper%20as%20Luther%20in%20season%20four%2C%20episode%20four%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Umbrella%20Academy.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b3a395955b01c3294ca019%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221037%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETom%20Hopper%20as%20Luther%20in%20season%20four%2C%20episode%20four%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Umbrella%20Academy.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EChristos%20Kalohoridis%2FNetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20season%20four%20picks%20up%20several%20years%20after%20the%20timeline%20reset%2C%20Luther%20is%20shown%20capitalizing%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20has%20a%20normal%20human%20body%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20part-ape%20physique.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20seen%20flexing%20his%20muscles%20while%20performing%20a%20striptease%20at%20a%20quiet%20bar%20with%20few%20patrons.%20Although%20Luther%20isn't%20the%20smoothest%20or%20most%20natural%20professional%20dancer%2C%20the%20money%20is%20just%20enough%20for%20him%20to%20get%20by.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20the%20Umbrella%20Academy%20doesn't%20exist%20in%20this%20timeline%2C%20Luther%20squats%20at%20the%20%3Cspan%3Eabandoned%20and%20run-down%20Hargreeves%20Home%20for%20Wayward%20Boys.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDiego%20works%20at%20a%20parcel%20delivery%20service%20called%20RPS%20and%20lives%20in%20the%20suburbs.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221581%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22David%20Casta%C3%B1eda%20as%20Diego%20on%20season%20four%2C%20episode%20six%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Umbrella%20Academy.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b3c1d2955b01c3294cb0ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221186%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDavid%20Casta%C3%B1eda%20as%20Diego%20on%20season%20four%2C%20episode%20six%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Umbrella%20Academy.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESeason%20four%20kicks%20off%20with%20Diego%20and%20Lila%2C%20who%20revealed%20she%20was%20pregnant%20during%20the%20previous%20season%20finale%2C%20throwing%20a%20sixth%20birthday%20party%20for%20their%20eldest%20child%20Grace.%20Diego%20and%20Lila%20also%20have%20twins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20season%20progresses%2C%20we%20see%20the%20cracks%20in%20their%20relationship.%20Diego%20is%20insecure%20about%20his%20job%20and%20thinks%20his%20talents%20would%20be%20better%20served%20at%20the%20CIA.%20He's%20also%20unhappy%20living%20with%20his%20in-laws.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Lila%20leaves%20the%20house%20often%2C%20secretly%20going%20to%20meetings%20for%20a%20group%20known%20as%20The%20Keepers%20(who%20believe%20in%20the%20existence%20of%20other%20timelines)%20because%20she%20needs%20an%20escape%20from%20their%20%26quot%3Bsuburban%20hellscape.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20dinner%20in%20which%20Ben%20spikes%20the%20siblings'%20shots%20with%20marigold%2C%20Diego%20is%20thrilled%20about%20the%20return%20of%20his%20powers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELila%20struggles%20with%20the%20transition%20from%20a%20full-time%20assassin%20to%20a%20mother%20of%20three.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221561%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ritu%20Arya%20as%20Lila%20on%20season%20four%2C%20episode%20six%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Umbrella%20Academy.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b3c217955b01c3294cb124%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221171%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERitu%20Arya%20as%20Lila%20on%20season%20four%2C%20episode%20six%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Umbrella%20Academy.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20transition%20from%20full-time%20assassin%20to%20full-time%20caregiver%20to%20three%20small%20children%20and%20one%20chunky%20husband%20is%20no%20picnic%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20tells%20Five%20when%20they%20run%20into%20each%20other%20at%20a%20Keepers%20meeting%20in%20the%20season%20four%20premiere.%20%26quot%3BI%20needed%20to%20get%20outside%20the%20house%2C%20OK%3F%20I%20saw%20a%20sign%20and%20took%20a%20chance.%20It's%20cheaper%20than%20therapy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELila%20and%20Five%20go%20on%20to%20work%20undercover%20investigating%20The%20Keepers%20and%20the%20alternate%20timelines%2C%20agreeing%20to%20keep%20it%20a%20secret%20from%20Diego.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20episode%20three%2C%20Lila%20tells%20Diego%20that%20they%20need%20a%20break%20from%20each%20other%20to%20reassess%20their%20marriage.%20In%20the%20following%20episode%2C%20Lila%20tells%20Diego%20that%20she%20still%20loves%20him%2C%20but%20she's%20frustrated%20by%20his%20constant%20complaining%20about%20his%20job%20and%20his%20in-laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Lila%20and%20Five%20take%20a%20train%20that%20allows%20them%20to%20travel%20between%20alternate%20timelines%2C%20they%20get%20lost%20and%20are%20unable%20to%20find%20their%20way%20back%20to%20their%20universe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20stuck%20alone%20together%20for%20seven%20years%2C%20moving%20from%20timeline%20to%20timeline%2C%20sometimes%20getting%20chased%20or%20attacked%20in%20the%20process.%20Eventually%2C%20Lila%20gets%20tired%20of%20running%20so%20she%20and%20Five%20briefly%20settle%20down%20together%20in%20a%20timeline%20that%20has%20a%20serene%20greenhouse.%20They%20end%20up%20kissing%20and%20striking%20up%20a%20romance%2C%20which%20immediately%20ends%20once%20they%20find%20their%20way%20back%20to%20their%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20they%20spend%20years%20hopping%20from%20timeline%20to%20timeline%2C%20Lila%20and%20Five%20are%20only%20actually%20gone%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%20in%20their%20universe.%20Naturally%2C%20Diego%20is%20furious%20when%20he%20learns%20that%20Lila%20and%20Five%20carried%20out%20a%20secret%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20finale%2C%20Diego%20and%20Lila%20agree%20to%20send%20their%20kids%20and%20the%20in-laws%20to%20the%20train%20so%20they%20can%20escape%20the%20Cleanse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20before%20sacrificing%20themselves%2C%20the%20couple%20makes%20amends%2C%20with%20Diego%20saying%20that%20he%20finally%20sees%20her%20for%20who%20she%20is%20and%20Lila%20saying%20that%20she%20didn't%20mean%20to%20hurt%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAllison%20reunites%20with%20her%20daughter%20Claire.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Emmy%20Raver-Lampman%20as%20Allison%20on%20season%20four%2C%20episode%20four%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Umbrella%20Academy.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b3c022b4912df3ae19bf01%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEmmy%20Raver-Lampman%20as%20Allison%20on%20season%20four%2C%20episode%20four%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Umbrella%20Academy.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20season%20three%2C%20Allison%20finds%20herself%20reunited%20with%20her%20daughter%20Claire%20from%20the%20original%20timeline%20and%20her%20husband%20Raymond%20Chestnut%20whom%20she%20met%20in%20Dallas%20in%20the%201963%20timeline.%20It's%20unclear%20what%20exactly%20happens%20between%20Allison%20and%20Ray%2C%20but%20when%20season%20four%20picks%20up%20six%20years%20later%2C%20she's%20a%20single%20mom.%20In%20the%20third%20episode%2C%20Klaus%20makes%20a%20comment%20about%20how%20he%20took%20care%20of%20Allison%20%26quot%3Bsince%20Ray%20walked%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20reset%20timeline%2C%20Allison%20is%20still%20an%20actor.%20She's%20the%20face%20of%20a%20laundry%20detergent%20commercial%20but%20has%20bombed%20auditions%20and%20isn't%20exactly%20an%20A-lister.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegardless%20of%20her%20career%2C%20Claire%20continues%20to%20be%20her%20main%20priority.%20In%20the%20finale%2C%20she%20sends%20her%20daughter%20on%20the%20train%20with%20Lila's%20family%20so%20that%20she%20can%20live%20in%20a%20single%20utopian%20timeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20the%20reset%20timeline%2C%20Klaus%20is%20sober%2C%20a%20germaphobe%2C%20and%20a%20protective%20uncle%20to%20Claire.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221268%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Robert%20Sheehan%20as%20Klaus%20in%20season%20four%2C%20episode%20four%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Umbrella%20Academy.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b3c1e35da406397bf3f86f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22951%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERobert%20Sheehan%20as%20Klaus%20in%20season%20four%2C%20episode%20four%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Umbrella%20Academy.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20his%20power%20of%20immortality%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20connect%20with%20spirits%2C%20Klaus%20is%20liberated%20and%20happy.%20He's%20three%20years%20sober%20and%20lives%20life%20cautiously%2C%20keeping%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20Claire%20to%20protect%20her%20from%20the%20dangers%20of%20the%20world.%20He's%20also%20very%20wary%20of%20germs%2C%20wearing%20a%20face%20mask%20and%20gloves%20when%20he%20reconnects%20with%20the%20other%20siblings.%20Klaus%20embraces%20his%20power-less%20life%20because%20he's%20more%20responsible%20and%20trusted%20by%20his%20niece.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20Klaus%20finds%20himself%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20death%20in%20episode%20two%2C%20Allison%20makes%20him%20drink%20marigold%20(the%20element%20that%20gives%20the%20siblings%20their%20power).%20After%20Klaus'%20powers%20return%2C%20he%20gets%20into%20a%20dicey%20situation%20with%20a%20man%20named%20Quinn%2C%20whom%20he%20owes%20%2440%2C000.%20Klaus%20ends%20up%20getting%20buried%20alive.%20Luckily%2C%20he's%20able%20to%20bust%20out%20of%20the%20casket%20at%20the%20same%20moment%20that%20Allison%20digs%20up%20the%20grave%20to%20save%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKlaus%20aptly%20sums%20up%20his%20relationship%20with%20his%20family%20in%20the%20finale%2C%20just%20before%20their%20sacrifice%2C%20telling%20them%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20you%20guys%2C%20but%20you%20are%20all%20assholes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EViktor%20creates%20a%20new%20life%20for%20himself%20far%20away%20from%20his%20siblings%20in%20Nova%20Scotia%2C%20Canada.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221588%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elliot%20Page%20as%20Viktor%20on%20season%20four%2C%20episode%20four%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Umbrella%20Academy.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b3c1ec955b01c3294cb0fc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221191%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElliot%20Page%20as%20Viktor%20on%20season%20four%2C%20episode%20four%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Umbrella%20Academy.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EViktor%20becomes%20the%20owner%20of%20a%20bar%20in%20Nova%20Scotia%20and%20enjoys%20the%20distance%20from%20his%20family%2C%20but%20he%20reluctantly%20agrees%20to%20go%20to%20Grace's%20birthday%20party.%20However%2C%20he%20doesn't%20make%20it%20to%20the%20party%20because%20he's%20kidnapped%20by%20a%20mysterious%20man%20named%20Sy%20Grossman%2C%20who%20uses%20the%20tactic%20as%20a%20way%20to%20get%20the%20Umbrella%20Academy%20members'%20attention%20and%20ask%20for%20help%20retrieving%20Jennifer%2C%20whom%20he%20claims%20is%20his%20estranged%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20in%20the%20season%2C%20when%20the%20siblings%20go%20to%20Reginald%20Hargreeves%20(Colm%20Feore)%20for%20help%2C%20Viktor%20unleashes%20years%20of%20rage%20and%20resentment%20that%20he's%20kept%20inside%20regarding%20this%20father.%20This%20version%20of%20Reginald%20isn't%20the%20same%20one%20who%20raised%20him%2C%20but%20he's%20similarly%20blunt%20and%20detached.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20episode%20five%2C%20Viktor%20saves%20Reginald%20from%20getting%20shot.%20In%20response%2C%20he%20tells%20Viktor%20that%20the%20other%20Reginald%20was%20wrong%20to%20treat%20Viktor%20like%20an%20outcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBen%20is%20a%20far%20more%20prominent%20character%20in%20season%20four%2C%20and%20the%20%26quot%3BJennifer%20incident%26quot%3B%20is%20finally%20explained.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222003%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Justin%20H.%20Min%20as%20Ben%20on%20season%20four%2C%20episode%20two%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Umbrella%20Academy.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b3c1f6955b01c3294cb107%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221502%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJustin%20H.%20Min%20as%20Ben%20Hargreeves%20on%20season%20four%2C%20episode%20two%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Umbrella%20Academy.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20version%20of%20Ben%20in%20season%20four%20is%20from%20the%20Sparrow%20Academy%20in%20another%20timeline%2C%20so%20the%20Hargreeves%20aren't%20his%20siblings.%20This%20version%20of%20Ben%20was%20convicted%20in%202019%20for%20a%20crypto%20scam%20and%20served%20four%20years%20in%20Avalon%20Federal%20Correctional%20Institution.%20When%20he's%20released%20on%20probation%2C%20Luther%20picks%20him%20up%20from%20prison%2C%20and%20Ben%20inevitably%20gets%20roped%20into%20the%20siblings'%20hijinks%20%E2%80%94%20name