0hunt%20Ben%20and%20Jennifer%20because%20one%20of%20the%20hosts%20must%20be%20eliminated%20before%20the%20reaction%20is%20complete.%20Reginald%20is%20too%20late%2C%20though%2C%20because%20Ben%20and%20Jennifer%20make%20out%20and%20their%20powers%20collide%2C%20triggering%20the%20Cleanse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20virus%20eventually%20takes%20over%20both%20their%20bodies%20and%20they%20morph%20into%20a%20large%2C%20grotesque%20creature%20that%20grows%20exponentially.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFive%20figures%20out%20the%20key%20to%20preventing%20the%20end%20of%20the%20world.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221906%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aidan%20Gallagher%20as%20Five%20on%20season%20four%2C%20episode%20four%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Umbrella%20Academy.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b3c08a955b01c3294cb059%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221300%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAidan%20Gallagher%20as%20Five%20on%20season%20four%2C%20episode%20four%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Umbrella%20Academy.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20finale%2C%20Five%20travels%20to%20another%20timeline%20and%20encounters%20various%20versions%20of%20himself.%20One%20of%20these%20alternate%20Fives%20explains%20that%20there's%20only%20supposed%20to%20be%20one%20timeline.%20Instead%2C%20the%20original%20timeline%20was%20shattered%20into%20an%20infinite%20number%20of%20alternate%20timelines%20in%20an%20infinite%20loop%20of%20time.%20All%20the%20alternate%20Fives%20have%20given%20up%20on%20trying%20to%20fix%20the%20issue%20because%20the%20problem%20is%20the%20Hargreeves%20siblings%2C%20who%20are%20doomed%20to%20save%20or%20destroy%20the%20world%20repeatedly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Five%20returns%20to%20the%20main%20timeline%2C%20he%20tells%20his%20siblings%20that%20their%20births%20are%20what%20caused%20the%20creation%20of%20multiple%20timelines.%20When%20their%20birth%20