rl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-confirms-discovering-worlds-first-large-shallow-gas-field-in-disputed-south-china-sea%2Famp_articleshow%2F112373990.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Antim%20Panghal%20Breaks%20Silence%20On%20Reports%20Of%20Her%2C%20Sister's%20Arrest%20In%20Paris%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20wrestler%20Antim%20Panghal%20refuted%20the%20rumours%20of%20her%20and%20her%20sister's%20arrest%20in%20Paris.%20After%20Antim's%200-10%20loss%20against%20Turkey's%20Yetgil%20Zeynep%2C%20it%20was%20reported%20that%20she%20tried%20to%20sneak%20her%20sister%20into%20the%20Olympic%20Games%20village%20using%20her%20accreditation%20card%20but%20was%20detained%20by%20the%20French%20police.%20However%2C%20Antim%20has%20now%20revealed%20that%20no%20such%20thing%20happened.%20While%20it%20is%20true%20that%20her%20sister%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20police%20station%2C%20Antim%20said%20that%20it%20only%20happened%20as%20the%20police%20wanted%20to%20verify%20her%20true%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20shared%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fnnis_sports%2Fstatus%2F1821457298826387964%3Ft%3DIcc-F44r3c7zXArDdt5cSQ%26s%3D19%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENNIS%20Sports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Antim%20revealed%20that%20it%20was%20she%20who%20went%20to%20her%20sister's%20hotel%20after%20falling%20sick.%20Since%20she%20had%20forgotten%20some%20of%20her%20stuff%20at%20the%20Games%20village%2C%20she%20asked%20her%20sister%20Nisha%20to%20get%20the%20things%20from%20the%20village%2C%20which%20is%20when%20the%20entire%20trouble%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20wasn't%20my%20day%20yesterday%2C%20as%20I%20lost%20my%20bout.%20But%2C%20since%20I've%20lost%2C%20talks%20are%20going%20on%20that%20my%20sister%20has%20been%20arrested%20by%20the%20police%2C%20or%20I've%20been%20arrested%20by%20the%20police%2C%20nothing%20of%20that%20sort%20has%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20Antim%20said%20in%20a%20video%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20lost%20my%20bout%20yesterday%2C%20I%20got%20a%20fever.%20My%20sister%2C%20who%20has%20been%20living%20in%20a%20hotel%2C%20wanted%20to%20take%20me%20there.%20I%20had%20taken%20permission%20from%20my%20coaches%20to%20go%20with%20her%2C%20as%20I%20wasn't%20feeling%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20gave%20me%20permission%20and%20I%20came%20to%20the%20hotel.%20When%20I%20came%20here%2C%20I%20needed%20some%20of%20my%20stuff%20which%20was%20still%20in%20the%20Olympic%20Village.%20As%20I%20was%20unwell%2C%20I%20slept.%20My%20sister%20took%20my%20accreditation%20card%20and%20went%20to%20the%20village.%20She%20asked%20the%20authorities%20there%20if%20she%20was%20allowed%20to%20get%20my%20stuff%20from%20the%20village.%20The%20authorities%20took%20away%20the%20accreditation%20card%20from%20her%20and%20took%20her%20to%20the%20police%20station%20for%20verification.%20This%20was%20the%20only%20reason%20she%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20police%20station.%20I%20wasn't%20taken%20to%20the%20police%20station%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAntim%20also%20revealed%20that%20her%20sister%20was%20released%20by%20the%20police%20soon%20after%20the%20verification%20was%20completed%20%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20verification%20was%20done%2C%20my%20sister%20was%20sent%20back%20with%20the%20accreditation%20card%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20rumour%20about%20Antim's%20coaches%20getting%20into%20a%20fight%20with%20a%20cab%20driver%20also%20surfaced.%20She%20shed%20light%20on%20the%20incident%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20also%20said%20that%20my%20coach%20fought%20with%20a%20driver%20but%20that%20isn't%20true%20either.%20My%20coaches%20were%20just%20upset%20with%20my%20loss.%20I%20was%20the%20one%20who%20booked%20their%20cab.%20They%20came%20to%20the%20hotel%20but%20got%20into%20a%20bit%20of%20trouble%20because%20of%20a%20language%20barrier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20wanted%20to%20come%20to%20the%20hotel%20to%20collect%20money%20(Euros)%20but%20some%20miscommunication%20happened%20with%20the%20cab%20driver.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20my%20coaches%20came%20to%20the%20room%20to%20collect%20money%20and%20since%20the%20room%20was%20high%20up%20in%20the%20building%2C%20it%20took%20some%20time.%20The%20delay%20resulted%20in%20a%20bit%20of%20an%20argument%20with%20the%20cab%20driver%2C%20but%20nothing%20major%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20her%20return%20is%20concerned%2C%20the%20federation%20had%20booked%20her%20flight%20from%20Paris%20soon%20after%20her%20elimination%20from%20the%20Paris%20Games%20was%20confirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20my%20return%20to%20India%2C%20it%20was%20I%20who%20told%20the%20federation%20to%20book%20my%20flight%20for%20today%20or%20tomorrow.%20They%20had%20already%20done%20that.%20I%20request%20all%20of%20you%20to%20not%20spread%20rumours%2C%20as%20my%20time%20here%20has%20already%20been%20torrid.%20Thank%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723111740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-08%2Fuv18s31o_antim-panghal_625x300_20_August_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fwrestler-antim-panghal-breaks-silence-on-reports-of-her-sisters-arrest-in-paris-6291826%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20wrestler%20Antim%20Panghal%20dismissed%20rumours%20of%20her%20and%20her%20sister's%20arrest%20in%20Paris%20but%20confirmed%20that%20the%20latter%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20police%20station%20because%20of%20some%20verification.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fwrestler-antim-panghal-breaks-silence-on-reports-of-her-sisters-arrest-in-paris-6291826%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Deleted%20scene%20from%20Ranbir%20's%20'Animal'%20goes%20VIRAL%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publishe