t%20and%20starting%20businesses%20instead.%20Among%20people%2055%20and%20older%20who%20started%20a%20business%20in%202023%2C%2044%25%20said%20they%20wanted%20more%20flexibility%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20their%20work%20schedule%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%2041%25%20said%20they%20believed%20they%20had%20a%20business%20opportunity%2C%20according%20to%20data%20shared%20with%20Business%20Insider%20by%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGusto%2C%20a%20payroll%20services%20company%20for%20small%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGusto%20surveyed%201%2C345%20new%20business%20owners%20of%20all%20ages%20between%20late%20January%20and%20early%20March%20using%20its%20payroll%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcCaman%2C%20now%2070%2C%20is%20the%20vice%20president%20and%20chief%20strategy%20officer%20at%20Orion%20Therapeutics.%20McCaman%20said%20Orion's%20biotech%20field%20is%20risky%20yet%20meaningful%20and%20received%20particular%20interest%20after%20the%20development%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20vaccines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20works%20remotely%20outside%20Frederick%2C%20Maryland%2C%20while%20the%20rest%20of%20his%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eteam%20is%20based%20in%20Knoxville%2C%20Tennessee.%20McCaman%20is%20passionate%20about%20staying%20engaged%20with%20his%20interests%20and%20said%20remote%20work%20has%20enabled%20him%20to%20extend%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCall%20it%20semi-retired%20if%20you%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20McCaman%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20actually%20a%20fun%20time%20to%20sit%20back%20and%20go%2C%20'Okay%2C%20what%20can%20I%20do%3F%20What%20is%20still%20fun%20to%20do%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229a46e042-ed02-4896-8c3e-d646c14d1cd5%5C%22%3EStarting%20a%20business%20at%2068%20and%20%3Cstrong%3Efinding%20purpose%20in%20'semi-retirement'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMcCaman%20studied%20chemistry%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%20San%20Diego%20before%20earning%20his%20Ph.D.%20in%20biochemistry%20from%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Davis.%20He%20enjoyed%20a%20decadeslong%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecareer%20working%20in%20biotech%20in%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20in%202011%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMcCaman%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20new%20job%20and%20said%20he%20needed%20a%20change.%20McCaman%20and%20his%20wife%20packed%20up%20their%20things%20and%20drove%20across%20the%20country%2C%20with%20McCaman%20chasing%20potential%20job%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eoffers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20year%2C%20he%20landed%20a%20position%20at%20Lonza%2C%20a%20manufacturing%20company%20in%20Maryland%2C%20where%20he%20worked%20as%20head%20of%20cell%20development.%20After%20four%20years%2C%20he%20switched%20jobs%20again.%20From%202015%20until%202020%2C%20McCaman%20was%20vice%20president%20of%20process%20development%20at%20Intellia%20Therapeutics%2C%20a%20biotech%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20his%20time%20at%20Intellia%20reinvigorated%20his%20passion%20for%20scientific%20research%2C%20and%20in%20March%202020%2C%20McCaman%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20began%20consulting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20consulting%20picked%20up%2C%20it%20was%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20the%20world%20is%20still%20out%20there%2C%20and%20I%20can%20be%20a%20part%20of%20it%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20McCaman%20met%20Trey%20Fischer%2C%20then%20a%20recent%20Ph.D.%20graduate%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Tennessee.%20McCaman%20and%20Fischer%20launched%20Orion%20with%20Deidra%20Mountain%2C%20a%20University%20of%20Tennessee%20professor%2C%20and%20Jennifer%20Zachry%2C%20a%20graduate%20student.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcCaman%20put%20up%20the%20first%20%2410%2C000%20investment%20for%20Orion%20and%2C%20in%20July%2C%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.knoxnews.com%2Fstory%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2024%2F07%2F09%2Funiversity-of-tennessee-chooses-orion-therapeutics-first-for-5m-fund%2F74330014007%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereceived%20%24300%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E%20fro