r%20buying%20a%20sailboat%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20relocate%20to%20Europe%20and%20explore%20as%20many%20destinations%20as%20they%20could%20without%20breaking%20the%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20now%20live%20on%20their%20boat%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvintage-photochrom-images-of-french-italian-riviera-and-monaco-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFrench%20Riviera%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20Doug%20said%20is%20cheaper%20than%20living%20in%20the%20US.%20Both%20still%20work%2C%20but%20they%20plan%20on%20retiring%20within%20two%20years.%20Doug%20asked%20to%20use%20his%20first%20name%20because%20his%20company%20doesn't%20know%20about%20his%20relocation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20lives%20are%20much%20fuller%20of%20amazing%20sites%20and%20places%20to%20visit%2C%20much%20easier%20than%20coming%20all%20the%20way%20from%20the%20US%2C%20with%20castles%20everywhere%2C%20little%20villages%20in%20Provence%20and%20throughout%20Italy%2C%20and%20Michelin%20star%20restaurants%20all%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20Doug%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2298a8c5f1-7a77-44f2-ab20-d210f8567449%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELeaving%20the%20US%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDoug%20was%20born%20and%20raised%20in%20Boston%2C%20where%20he%20started%20as%20a%20professional%20photographer.%20He%20moved%20to%20California%20to%20set%20up%20his%20studio%2C%20though%20he%20decided%20to%20leave%20the%20industry%20and%20find%20more%20stable%20employment.%20He%20saw%20an%20advertisement%20in%20the%20paper%20for%20a%20nine-month%20course%20reviewing%20three%20coding%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20next%20four%20decades%2C%20Doug%20worked%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%20and%20consultant%20for%20various%20companies.%20He%20moved%20across%20the%20country%20for%20work%2C%20from%20Dallas%20to%20Indianapolis%20to%20Maine.%20He%20returned%20to%20New%20England%2C%20building%20his%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20and%20rising%20the%20ranks.%20His%20income%20