%20hearing%20into%20the%20incident%20in%20which%20a%20Boeing%20737%20Max%20lost%20its%20door%20panel%20shortly%20after%20takeoff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20investigators%2C%20the%20captain%20of%20the%20flight%2C%20whose%20name%20was%20redacted%20along%20with%20other%20crew%20members%2C%20described%20a%20%26quot%3Bloud%20bang%2C%20ears%20popping%2C%20my%20head%20got%20pushed%20up%20into%20the%20HUD%20%5Bhead-up%20display%5D%20and%20my%20headset%20got%20pushed%20off%E2%80%A6%20almost%20off%20my%20head.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20captain%20said%20they%20saw%20one%20of%20the%20plane's%20flight%20attendants%20%26quot%3Bthrown%20to%20the%20floor%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20force%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bexplosive%20experience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20flight's%20first%20officer%2C%20who%20was%20also%20interviewed%20by%20regulators%2C%20described%20the%20moments%20after%20the%20blowout%20as%20%26quot%3Bchaos%26quot%3B%20as%20cabin%20crew%20scrambled%20to%20deal%20with%20an%20emergency%20at%2016%2C000%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20hear%20much%2C%20it%20was%20very%20loud%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%20%26quot%3BAt%20that%20point%20my%20focus%20was%20forward%2C%20and%20I%20yelled%20get%20down%2C%20get%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20plane's%20flight%20attendants%20said%20they%20heard%20%26quot%3Ba%20really%20loud%20bang%20and%20lots%20of%20whooshing%20air.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20described%20the%20moment%20they%20realized%20there%20was%20a%20hole%20in%20the%20plane%2C%20telling%20investigators%20that%20they%20thought%20that%20some%20passengers%20had%20been%20sucked%20out%20of%20the%20passenger%20jet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20point%20where%20I%20first%20saw%20the%20hole%2C%20I%20saw%20five%20empty%20seats.%20In%20that%20moment%E2%80%A6%20I%20was%20absolutely%20certain%20that%20we%20had%20lost%20people%20out%20of%20the%20hole%20and%20that%20we%20had%20casualties%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp