n.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhattacharjee%2C%20also%20a%20former%20member%20of%20the%20CPM's%20top%20decision-making%20body%2C%20Politburo%2C%20served%20as%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20from%202000%20to%202011%2C%20succeeding%20Jyoti%20Basu%20in%20the%20top%20post.%20Mr%20Bhattacharjee%20led%20the%20CPM%20into%20the%202011%20state%20polls%2C%20when%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee-led%20Trinamool%20Congress%20posted%20a%20historic%20win%2C%20ending%20the%2034-year%20Communist%20rule%20in%20the%20eastern%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20for%20his%20simple%20lifestyle%2C%20Mr%20Bhattacharjee%20breathed%20his%20last%20at%20the%20two-bedroom%20flat%20at%20Palm%20Avenue%20from%20where%20he%20once%20ran%20the%20state.%20His%20organs%20will%20be%20donated%20for%20medical%20research%20as%20per%20his%20wishes.%20His%20body%20will%20be%20kept%20in%20the%20CPM%20headquarters%20for%20his%20followers%20to%20pay%20respects%20and%20the%20last%20journey%20will%20take%20place%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20alumnus%20of%20Presidency%20College%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20Mr%20Bhattacharjee%20was%20a%20school%20teacher%20before%20he%20joined%20politics%20full-time.%20After%20serving%20as%20an%20MLA%20and%20a%20state%20minister%2C%20he%20was%20elevated%20to%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20before%20Mr%20Basu%20stepped%20down%20in%202000.%20As%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20he%20led%20the%20CPM%20to%20Assembly%20poll%20victories%20in%202001%20and%202006.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20Mr%20Bhattacharjee's%20tenure%2C%20the%20Left%20Front%20government%20adopted%20a%20relatively%20open%20policy%20towards%20business%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20Jyoti%20Basu%20regime.%20Ironically%2C%20it%20was%20this%20policy%20and%20land%20acquisitions%20related%20to%20industrialisation%20that%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20the%20Left's%20stunning%20defeat%20in%20the%202011%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%2C%20which%20won%20just%2030%20seats%20in%20the%202006%20elections%2C%20led%20the%20movement%20against%20the%20Tata%20Motors%20plant%20in%20Singur.%20Eventually%2C%20in%202008%2C%20Ratan%20Tata%20decided%20to%20shift%20the%20project%20to%20Gujarat%20and%20cited%20the%20movement%20by%20Ms%20Banerjee%20as%20the%20reason.%20This%20was%20a%20big%20setback%20to%20Mr%20Bhattacharjee's%20government.%C2%A0Equally%20damaging%20was%20the%20violence%20in%20Nandigram%20where%20police%20action%20against%20a%20group%20protesting%20against%20land%20acquisition%20for%20a%20chemical%20hub%20project%20led%20to%2014%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee's%20Trinamool%20Congress%20reaped%20the%20political%20dividends%20of%20the%20anti-incumbency%20of%20the%20Left%20Front%20rule%20and%20the%20negative%20perception%20about%20the%20state%20government's%20land%20acquisition%20policies%2C%20winning%20184%20seats%20in%20the%202011%20election.%20The%20Left's%20defeat%20in%20the%202011%20polls%20started%20a%20decline%20it%20is%20yet%20to%20recover%20from.%20Over%20the%20next%20decade%2C%20the%20BJP%20overtook%20it%20as%20the%20main%20Opposition%20and%20the%20Left%20now%20is%20reduced%20to%20a%20minor%20force%20in%20the%20state%20it%20once%20ruled%20unchallenged%20for%20decades.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal%20Governor%20CV%20Ananda%20Bose%20expressed%20his%20condolences%20to%20Mr%20Bhattacharjee's%20family.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20he%20was%20saddened%20by%20the%20news.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20a%20political%20stalwart%20who%20served%20the%20state%20with%20commitment.%20My%20heartfelt%20condolences%20to%20his%20family%20and%20supporters.%20Om%20Shanti%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20tweeted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20condolence%20message%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Banerjee%20said%20she%20had%20a%20decades-long%20association%20with%20the%20veteran%20Left%20leader.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20very%20upset.%20My%20condolences%20to%20Meera%20di%2C%20Suchetan%20and%20to%20all%20supporters%20of%20CPM.%20We%20have%20already%20taken%20a%20decision%20that%20we%20shall%20give%20him%20full%20respect%20and%20ceremonial%20honour%20during%20his%20last%20journey%20and%20rites%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20the%20Opposition%2C%20BJP's%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%2C%20said%20he%20is%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20saddened%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20news%20and%20expressed%20his%20condolences%20to%20Mr%20Bhattacharjee's%20family%20and%20admirers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELong-time%20comrade%20and%20CPM%20general%20secretary%20Sitaram%20Yechury%20described%20the%20news%20of%20Mr%20Bhattacharjee's%20death%20as%20%26quot%3Bshattering%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BHis%20dedication%20to%20the%20party%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20our%20shared%20ideals%20and%20also%20his%20ability%20to%20look%20ahead%20will%20always%20function%20as%20a%20lodestar%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723109760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-04%2Fbuddhadeb-bhattacharjee_650x400_41461089849.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fformer-west-bengal-chief-minister-buddhadeb-bhattacharya-dies-at-80-6289675%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Buddhadeb%20Bhattacharjee%2C%20veteran%20Left%20leader%20and%20former%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20died%20at%20his%20south%20Kolkata%20residence%20this%20morning.%20He%20was%2080.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fformer-west-bengal-chief-minister-buddhadeb-bhattacharya-dies-at-80-6289675%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Speaker's%20powers%20under%20threat'%3A%20Akhilesh%20in%20LS%3B%20Amit%20Shah%20responds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723109643000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112372671%2Cimgsize-1101676.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Famit-shah-vs-akhilesh-yadav-in-lok-sabha-akhilesh-alleges-speakers-rig