f%20invoices.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20summer%202024%2C%20they%20expect%20to%20complete%201%2C000%20barbecue%20cleanings%20and%20generate%20CA%24150%2C000%20(about%20%24109%2C000)%20in%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20shared%20four%20strategies%20that%20helped%20them%20scale%20from%20a%20one-man%20operation%20to%20a%20business%20that%20employs%2020%20students%20and%20operates%20in%20six%20cities%20across%20southern%20Ontario.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2281e6820d-6dff-454c-a99f-c7d452667d5b%5C%22%3E1.%20Lean%20on%20mentors%20and%20build%20partnerships%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20teen%20entrepreneurs%20are%20well%20aware%20of%20their%20age%20and%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20no%20lawyer%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%2019%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20legal%20side%20of%20running%20and%20owning%20a%20business%20is%20a%20big%20portion.%20We've%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20help%20with%20that%2C%20especially%20in%20terms%20of%20building%20out%20contracts%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shaidle%2C%20thanks%20to%20their%20business%20mentor%2C%20who%20owns%20a%20small%20home-service%20business%20called%20Insight%20Pest.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20basically%20done%20everything%20we're%20looking%20to%20do%2C%20so%20he%20has%20insight%20on%20everything%20in%20terms%20of%20growing%20the%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20token%20of%20appreciation%2C%20Shaidle%20and%20Giffen%20cross-promote%20Insight%20Pest%20by%20including%20its%20logo%20on%20the%20merch%20they%20made%20for%20their%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20cross-promote%20two%20other%20companies%2C%20whom%20they%20consider%20%26quot%3Bsponsors.%26quot%3B%20One%20is%20a%20small%20business%20called%20Strodes%2C%20a%20butcher%20shop%20deli%20that%20makes%20its%20own%20all-natural%2C%20chemical-free%20degreaser%20that%20Shaidle%20Cleaning%20buys%20in%20bulk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20is%20an%20insurance%20company%20that%20helps%20them%20navigate%20the%20world%20of%20insurance%20and%20understand%20what%20coverage%20they%20need%2C%20said%20Shaidle%3A%20%26quot%3BBarbecue%20cleaning%20is%20not%20a%20very%20common%20thing%20you%20hear%20about%2C%20and%20so%20with%20insurance%20companies%2C%20it's%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20challenging%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20the%20cost%20would%20be%20and%20what%20the%20dangers%20are.%20We're%20working%20with%20a%20machine%20that%20produces%20flame%2C%20and%20also%20pressure%20washers%2C%20drills%2C%20and%20power%20tools.%20There%20are%20dangers%20with%20that%2C%20and%20it's%20always%20better%20safe%20than%20sorry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e54b8943-417f-4577-8342-69b7489f7882%5C%22%3E2.%20Go%20digital%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20first%20two%20summers%20in%20business%2C%20Shaidle%20acquired%20clients%20through%20door-knocking%20and%20word-of-mouth.%20He%20didn't%20go%20digital%20until%20Giffen%20joined%20the%20team%2C%20set%20up%20a%20website%20and%20email%20account%2C%20created%20a%20logo%2C%20and%20started%20posting%20content%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20built%20our%20website%20up%2C%20and%20Aran%20started%20doing%20SEO%20and%20Facebook%20ads%2C%20that%20was%20when%20we%20were%20really%20able%20to%20expand%20to%20different%20cities%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shaidle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221860%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22shaidle%20cleaning%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b3e0d05da406397bf40b57%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221395%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGiffen%20(left)%20and%20Shaidle%20speak%20to%20younger%20students%20about%20entrepreneurship.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Shaidle%20Cleaning%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGiffen%20also%20took%20it%20upon%20himself%20to%20contact%20a%20few%20news%20outlets%2C%20including%20the%20Hamilton%20Spectator.%20The%20publication%20ran%20an%20article%20in%20August%202023%2C%20and%20it%20immediately%20impacted%20business.%20Shaidle%20was%20working%20at%20a%20client's%20home%20when%20the%20story%20went%20live%20and%20recalls%20getting%20about%2050%20calls%20during%20the%20three-hour%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJake%20was%20getting%20calls%2C%20but%20we%20also%20had%20a%20form%20on%20our%20website%2C%20and%20so%20simultaneously%2C%20I%20had%20the%20Shaidle%20Cleaning%20email%20blowing%20up%20with%20120%2B%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20recalled%20Giffen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20taught%20them%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20no%20geographical%20boundary%20to%20online%20stories%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Shaidle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226c84f17d-8f67-4eb8-9a14-ccbea7388a93%5C%22%3E3.%20Automate%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShaidle%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20has%20freed%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20his%20own%20time%20thanks%20to%20a%20software%20called%20Jobber%2C%20which%20automatically%20messages%20clients%20about%20their%20appointments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20past%20three%20years%2C%20I%20was%20messaging%20everybody%20individually%20and%20then%20doing%20back-and-forth%20with%20everyone%20to%20see%20when%20they%20were%20around%20and%20when%20I%20was%20around%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Now%2C%20clients%20can%20book%20online%20and%20will%20receive%20a%20confirmation%20email%2C%20a%20reminder%20closer%20to%20their%20appointment%2C%20and%20a%20final%20email%20after%20the%20cleaning%20with%20their%20invoice%20attached.%20They'll%20also%20be%20prompted%20to%20leave%20a%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20creates%20really%20good%20customer%20service%2C%20but%20is%20not%20something%20that%20we%20have%20to%20do%20directly%20and%20spend%20time%20messaging%2014%20clients%20a%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a529be5d-a201-4bb7-b0cf-13c9e05b1c82%5C%22%3E4.%20Build%20a%20rock-solid%20team%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20way%20Shaidle%20and%20Giffen%20have%20freed%20up%20more%20time%20to%20focus%20on%20scaling%20is%20by%20expanding%20their%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20itself%20is%20time-intensive%3A%20Each%20cleaning%20takes%20about%20four%20hours%2