20suddenly%20thrust%20into%20live%20deals%20and%20meetings%20with%20clients.%20He%20was%20also%20asked%20to%20speak%20out%20and%20provide%20his%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSenior%20leaders%20were%20constantly%20coming%20out%20to%20the%20bullpen%20and%20asking%20the%20most%20junior%20person%20on%20the%20team%20what%20they%20thought%20about%20the%20deals%20that%20we%20were%20currently%20in%20process%20with%2C%20what%20they%20thought%20about%20up-and-coming%20trends%2C%20and%20where%20were%20some%20areas%20where%20the%20firm%20should%20be%20looking%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Plumlee%2C%20who%20interned%20with%20Blackstone%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202022%20and%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlumlee%20said%20one%20senior%20leader%20explained%20it%20to%20him%20this%20way%3A%20%26quot%3BYou're%20one%20of%20us%20now%2C%20and%20you're%20all%20here%20for%20a%20reason%3A%20We%20want%20to%20hear%20your%20thoughts.%20Rank%20doesn't%20matter%20here%2C%20your%20thoughts%20are%20just%20as%20valuable%20as%20the%20next%20guy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a2088ae6-e7e3-49dc-a79f-abd97f4e7128%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BWork%20harder%2C%20care%20more%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWall%20Street%20is%20notorious%20for%20its%20long%20hours%2C%20which%20can%20challenge%20early%20career%20workers%20and%20test%20their%20motivation%20and%20endurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlackstone%20is%20no%20different%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bday-in-the-life%26quot%3B%20video%20posted%20to%20the%20firm's%20LinkedIn%20earlier%20this%20year.%20In%20the%20video%2C%20summer%20analysts%20explain%20how%20they%20like%20to%20get%20to%20the%20office%20early%20to%20go%20through%20emails%20or%20otherwise%20prepare%20for%20the%20day.%20The%20video%20also%20shows%20interns%20eating%20both%20breakfast%20and%20dinner%20at%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20group%20photo%20of%20Blackstone's%20summer%20analyst%20class%20during%20orientation.%20Many%20people%20in%20chairs%20and%20formal%20dress%20smile%20at%20the%20camera.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a93fbbfb6d32635ee50de1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221257%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20group%20photo%20of%20Blackstone's%20summer%20analyst%20class%20during%20orientation.%3Cp%3EBlackstone%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Gray%2C%20in%20his%20speech%2C%20said%20that%20making%20an%20impression%20at%20Blackstone%20requires%20more%20than%20just%20racking%20up%20more%20hours%20than%20your%20peers.%20He%20compared%20success%20in%20business%20to%20success%20in%20sports%20or%20in%20the%20performance%20arts%2C%20saying%20that%20sometimes%20it%20just%20comes%20down%20to%20how%20much%20you%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20great%20performers%2C%20they're%20just%20out%20there%20practicing%20more%2C%20they%20get%20in%20a%20little%20bit%20earlier%2C%20they%20double%20triple%20check%20their%20work%2C%20they're%20not%20just%20punching%20the%20clock%2C%20they%20genuinely%20care%20about%20what%20they're%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20Gray%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHiring%20people%20with%20the%20right%20motivation%20is%20so%20important%20to%20the%20firm%20that%20it's%20part%20of%20the%20campus-recruiting%20process%2C%20Taylor%20Kanfer%2C%20managing%20director%20of%20human%20resources%20and%20head%20of%20campus%20recruiting%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20all%20evaluating%20for%20potential%2C%20but%20again%2C%20we're%20really%20looking%20for%20people%20who%20have%20the%20desire%20and%20hunger%2C%26quot%3B%20Kanfer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226ecdc5d7-a28c-4021-ac75-0e53d93bd313%5C%22%3EOpen-mindedness%20is%20key%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20employees%20should%20be%20ready%20to%20share%20their%20opinions%20and%20contribute%20to%20the%20firm%20from%20the%20beginning%20of%20their%20careers%2C%20they%20shouldn't%20have%20an%20over-inflated%20sense%20of%20their%20own%20perspective.%20Instead%2C%20they%20should%20always%20be%20looking%20to%20grow%20and%20learn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoss%2C%20the%20HR%20head%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20%26quot%3Blearning%20agility%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bhumility%26quot%3B%20are%20keys%20to%20success%20at%20every%20level%20of%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20at%20my%20level%2C%20it's%20critical%20to%20know%20that%20I%20don't%20know%20everything%20and%20that%20I%20have%20the%20humility%20to%20know%20that%20I%20should%20be%20learning%20from%20people%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Ross%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlumlee%20didn't%20know%20much%20about%20business%20when%20he%20started%20at%20Blackstone%20and%20had%20never%20worked%20a%20full-time%20corporate%20job%20before.%20Desperate%20to%20learn%2C%20he%20asked%20the%20firm%20for%20an%20opportunity%20that%20would%20serve%20as%20a%20crash%20course%20to%20both%20the%20firm%20and%20industry.%20This%20landed%20him%20in%20the%20tactical%20opportunities%20group%2C%20which%20invests%20across%20asset%20classes%2C%20industries%20and%20geographies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20learning%20curves%20proved%20steep%20at%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20military%2C%20people%20love%20their%20acronyms%20to%20talk%20about%20a%20piece%20of%20equipment%20or%20a%20particular%20kind%20of%20strategy%2C%20or%20a%20doctrine%2C%20what%20have%20you.%20And%20I've%20noticed%20there's%20no%20shortage%20of%20that%20in%20the%20world%20of%20finance%20either%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20prospect%20of%20learning%20a%20whole%20new%20language%20was%20daunting%2C%20but%20he%20made%20it%20through%20and%20today%20has%20a%20full-time%20role%20with%20the%20tactical%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20military%20helped%20remind%20me%20that%20there%20is%20light%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20tunnel%20once%20you%20can%20kind%20of%20cut%20through%20all%20this%20jargon%2C%26quot%3B%20Plumlee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221cd96f87-9931-40b6-9de6-60d39d43031f%5C%22%3EIt's%20a%20marathon%2C%20not%20a%20sprint%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Plumlee%20could%20give%20his%20former%20self%20any%20advice%2C%20it%20would%20be%20to%20lessen%20the%20pressure%20on%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20go%20back%20and%20talk%20to%20myself%20and%20tell%20myself%20to%20be%20patient%2C%26quot%3B%20Plumlee%20said.%26quot%3B%20I%20probably%20still%20wouldn't%20have%20been%2C%20but%20this%20has%20been%20very%20much%20a%20marathon%20and%20not%20a%20sprint.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20that%20end%2C%20he%20says%2C%20people%20would%20be%20wise%20to%20surround%20themselves%20with%20good%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTry%20to%20surround%20yourself%20with%20good%20people%20for%20that%20marathon%20and%20people%20that%20have%20similar%20goals%20and%20ambitions%20because%20you%20really%20can%20feed%20off%20one%20another%20in%20terms%20of%20what%20you%20teach%20each%20other%2C%20but%20you%20also%20drive%20one%20another%2C%26quot%3B%20Plumlee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20such%20strong%20connections%20with%20junior%20Blackstone%20employees%20that%20they%20even%20helped%20him%20prepare%20for%20applying%20to%20investment%20banking%20roles%20outside%20of%20Blackstone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20even%20interviewing%20to%20come%20back%20to%20the%20group%2C%20and%20they%20were%20helping%20me%20be%20the%20best%20version%20of%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20Plumlee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c228009e-544b-4929-8d78-02846ae96486%5C%22%3EIt's%20the%20soft%20skills%2C%20not%20the%20hard%20skills%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBlackstone%20has%20high%20standards%20and%20expects%20results%20from%20its%20employees.%20But%20it%20also%20doesn't%20expect%20early-career%20hires%20to%20have%20a%20full%20grasp%20of%20certain%20skills%2C%20like%20financial%20modeling%2C%20which%20they%20can%20learn%20on%20the%20job.%20When%20hiring%2C%20it%20prefers%20to%20focus%20on%20interpersonal%20skills%2C%20like%20leadership%2C%20according%20to%20Joe%20Zidle%2C%20ch