When%20she%20wasn't%20dancing%20competitively%2C%20she%20was%20on%20the%20cheer%20squad%20or%20running%20track.%20Now%2020%20and%20in%20college%2C%20Taylor%20belongs%20to%20two%20gyms%20in%20her%20hometown%20of%20Boca%20Raton%2C%20Florida%2C%20and%20goes%20five%20or%20six%20times%20a%20week.%20Though%20she%20has%20a%20busy%20schedule%20as%20a%20student%20studying%20communications%2C%20fitness%20has%20become%20one%20of%20her%20top%20priorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%202023%20survey%20from%20McKinsey%2C%20more%20than%20half%20of%20Gen%20Z%20respondents%20said%20fitness%20was%20a%20very%20high%20priority%20for%20them.%20Forty%20percent%20of%20all%20respondents%20said%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Taylor%2C%20these%20young%20people%20aren't%20just%20working%20out%20at%20home%20%E2%80%94%20they%20are%20helping%20drive%20up%20gym%20attendance.%20Surveys%20by%20the%20fitness%20organization%20Les%20Mills%20found%20that%20the%20share%20of%20adults%20who%20reported%20going%20to%20the%20gym%20increased%20to%2032%25%20in%202019%20from%2027%25%20in%202013.%20Other%20surveys%20and%20data%20from%20companies%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FPlacer.ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPlacer.ai%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20ABC%20Fitness%20similarly%20suggest%20more%20people%20are%20going%20to%20the%20gym%20more%20regularly%20than%20they%20did%20several%20years%20ago.%20And%20the%20memberships%20of%20chains%20like%20Planet%20Fitness%20have%20exploded%20%E2%80%94%20that%20brand%20gained%20more%20than%204%20million%20new%20members%20from%202019%20to%20the%20end%20of%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20much%20as%20we%20think%20that%20our%20country%20is%20obese%20or%20unhealthy%2C%20there's%20another%20whole%20side%20who%20are%20into%20their%20fitness%2C%26quot%3B%20Taylor%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20generation%20is%20taking%20that%20to%20the%20next%20step.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20particular%2C%20Gen%20Z%20loves%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworlds-strongest-man-shares-best-exercises-for-building-muscle-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elift%20weights%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20a%202022%20CivicScience%20survey%2C%20strength%20training%20was%20the%20most%20common%20type%20of%20workout%20cited%20by%20Gen%20Z%20respondents.%20And%20in%20a%202023%20survey%20in%20the%20American%20College%20of%20Sports%20Medicine's%20journal%2C%20it%20was%20ranked%20the%20second-most-popular%20fitness%20trend%20of%20the%20year.%20Taylor%20told%20me%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-start-lifting-weights-2018-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrength%20training%3C%2Fa%3E%20now%20makes%20up%2090%25%20of%20her%20routine.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20switch%20from%20my%20mom%2C%20who's%20been%20into%20cardio%20and%20being%20tiny%20and%20thin%2C%26quot%3B%20Taylor%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%20girls%20want%20big%20butts%20and%20big%20biceps.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffitness-has-exploded-into-a-nearly-100-billion-global-industry-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equest%20to%20get%20swole%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20one%20reason%20young%20people%20are%20showing%20up%20at%20the%20gym%20in%20droves%3A%20Weightlifting%20requires%20special%20equipment%20that%20is%20tricky%20to%20fit%20into%20a%20small%20apartment.%20But%20there%20are%20other%20pulls%3A%20At%20a%20time%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firl-social-startups-combat-loneliness-among-millennials-gen-z-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emeeting%20people%20can%20be%20challenging%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20an%20easy%20way%20to%20put%20yourself%20out%20there%20and%20make%20friends.%20Gyms%20are%20quickly%20becoming%20Gen%20Z's%20favorite%20hangout%20spot%20%E2%80%94%20but%20there's%20just%20one%20problem%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-americans-dont-exercise-mental-health-crisis-depression-anxiety-fitness-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efitness%20boom%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Chains%20like%20Planet%20Fitness%20rely%20on%20members%20never%20showing%20up%3B%20the%20gyms%20aren't%20built%20for%20Gen%20Z.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20Gen%20Z's%20exercise%20bug%20comes%20from%20social%20media%2C%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffitness-influencer-entrepreneurs-how-they-built-their-followings-customers-businesses-2020-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egymfluencers%20have%20taken%20off%3C%2Fa%3E.%20YouTube%20said%20that%20the%20number%20of%20fitness%20videos%20on%20its%20platform%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC9858650%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrew%20more%20than%20fivefold%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202020%20and%20that%20they've%20remained%20popular.%20Hundreds%20of%20personal%20trainers%2C%20amateur%20bodybuilders%2C%20and%20fitness-class%20instructors%20like%20Kayla%20Itsines%20(16%20million%20followers)%20and%20Christian%20Guzman%20(1%20million%20followers)%20have%20built%20loyal%20fanbases%20online%20by%20sharing%20their%20workout%20routines%2C%20swapping%20exercise%20tips%2C%20and%20showing%20off%20their%20tanned%20and%20toned%20muscles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20fitness-influencer%20culture%20is%20generally%20positive%20and%20aimed%20at%20educating%20people%20about%20their%20health%2C%20it%20can%20drift%20to%20the%20extreme.%20%26quot%3BGrindset%26quot%3B%20influencers%2C%20whose%20content%20converges%20the%20male-oriented%20online%20realm%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanosphere-widening-ideological-gap-between-young-men-women-gender-genz-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20manosphere%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20fitness-adjacent%20hustle-and-grind%20culture%2C%20have%20also%20exploded.%20Their%20mission%3F%20To%20self-optimize%20with%20routines%20like%20waking%20up%20at%204%20a.m.%2C%20running%2018%20miles%20fuelled%20only%20by%20black%20coffee%2C%20and%20listening%20to%20a%20business%20podcast%20at%20three%20times%20the%20speed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20influencer%20spectrum%20are%20trainers%20like%20Whitney%20Simmons%20(4%20million%20followers)%20and%20Simeon%20Panda%20(8%20million%20followers)%20who%20have%20helped%20bust%20the%20myths%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-lifting-better-than-cardio-body-builder-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elifting%20weights%20is%20only%20for%20men%20or%20that%20it%20just%20makes%20women%20bulky%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20think%20of%20the%20default%20approach%20to%20exercise%2C%20it%20almost%20always%20involves%20some%20form%20of%20cardio%3A%20walking%2C%20running%2C%20elliptical%20machines%2C%20spinning%2C%20cycling%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20fitness%20influencer%20Casey%20Johnston%20wrote%20in%20her%20popular%20newsletter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shesabeast.co%2Fcardio-has-fallen-strength-training-is-the-new-gold-standard-for-exercise-you-must-do%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShe's%20A%20Beast%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20emerging%20evidence%20suggests%20that%2C%20if%20anything%2C%20these%20exercise%20paradigms%20will%20soon%20be%20flipped.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnston%20used%20to%20think%20the%20low-calorie%2C%20high-cardio%20lifestyle%20was%20the%20way%20to%20go%20%E2%80%94%20but%20she%20eventually%20got%20frustrated%20that%20she%20wasn't%20seeing%20the%20physical%20results%20she%20had%20hoped%20for.%20Weightlifting%20helped%20her%20feel%20and%20look%20strong%20without%20needing%20to%20sacrifice%20her%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESarah%20Ryan%2C%20a%20personal%20trainer%20for%20the%20fitness%20app%20Ladder%2C%20thinks%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrength-training-better-cardio-burning-fat-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboom%20in%20weightlifting%3C%2Fa%3E%20simply%20stems%20from%20people%20learning%20that%20it's%20good%20for%20you.%20%26quot%3BBuilding%20muscle%20is%20going%20to%20favor%20a%20healthier%20body%20composition%2C%26quot%3B%20Ryan%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20more%20muscle%20mass%20you%20have%2C%20which%20is%20metabolically%20active%20tissue%2C%20the%20healthier%20you're%20going%20to%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20partly%20what%20motivated%20Amrita%20Bhasin%20to%20try%20weightlifting.%20The%2023-year-old%20first%20set%20foot%20in%20a%20gym%20when%20she%20moved%20from%20California%20to%20Portland%2C%20Maine%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%202023.%20Previously%2C%20Bhasin%20played%20tennis%2C%20pickleball%2C%20and%20field%20hockey.%20But%20after%20moving%20to%20a%20colder%20climate%2C%20she%20could%20no%20longer%20rely%20on%20her%20usual%20outdoor%20exercise%20routine.%20%26quot%3BIt%20didn't%20make%20sense%20for%20me%20to%20go%20to%20the%20gym%20just%20to%20run%20on%20the%20treadmill%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20That%20would%20be%20boring.%20So%2C%20inspired%20and%20encouraged%20by%20her%20male%20friends%20who%20started%20strength%20training%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20Bhasin%20started%20experimenting%20with%20lifting%20weights.%20%26quot%3BI'd%20grown%20up%20knowing%20the%20benefits%20of%20it%20for%20bone%20density%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20female%20friends%20who%20weightlift.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20winter%20in%20Maine%20gave%20her%20the%20opportunity%20to%20learn.%20When%20she%20started%20seeing%20the%20number%20on%20the%20weights%20go%20up%2C%20she%20became%20hooked.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%2080%2C%20the%20people%20who%20will%20be%20the%20most%20mobile%20will%20be%20those%20who%20did%20strength%20training%20when%20they%20were%20young%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20never%20used%20to%20be%20this%20education%20around%20it%2C%20for%20women%20especially%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BMore%20women%20need%20to%20be%20doing%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaylor%20also%20got%20into%20weightlifting%20after%20trying%20it%20out%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20%26quot%3BStrength%20training%20has%20the%20most%20return%20on%20investment%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20me%20when%20I%20asked%20why%20she%20likes%20it.%20%26quot%3BYou%20need%20continuous%20commitment%20in%20order%20to%20see%20results.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20seeing%20her%20biceps%20grow%20and%20her%20posture%20improve%2C%20Taylor%20started%20documenting%20her%20workout%20routines%20on%20a%20private%20Snapchat%20story%20for%20her%20friends.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20reaching%20out%20wanting%20to%20know%20what%20I%20do%2C%20what%20I%20eat.%20Then%20I%20thought%20maybe%20I%20need%20to%20showcase%20this%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20me.%20Now%20Taylor%20posts%20her%20workouts%20and%20other%20fitness-related%20content%20on%20Instagram%2C%20where%20she%20has%20amassed%20over%2030%2C000%20followers.%20She%20also%20writes%20about%20health%20on%20her%20blog%20Biceps%20By%20Britt.%20%26quot%3BMy%20goal%20is%20to%20show%20girls%20my%20age%20that%20it's%20good%20to%20lift%20heavy%20weights.%20It's%20good%20to%20eat%20high%20protein%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20health%20perks%20aren't%20the%20only%20reason%20young%20people%20are%20flocking%20to%20the%20gym%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20also%20one%20of%20the%20few%20places%20people%20regularly%20visit%20where%20they%20can%20meet%20new%20people.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20where%20their%20friends%20hang%20out%3B%20there's%20a%20sense%20of%20community%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jim%20Thomas%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20president%20of%20Fitness%20Management%20USA%2C%20a%20management-consulting%20firm%20specializing%20in%20the%20fitness%20and%20health%20club%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%202021%20McKinsey%20survey%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mckinsey.com%2Findustries%2Fconsumer-packaged-goods%2Four-insights%2Fsweating-for-the-fitness-consumer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E70%25%20of%20fitness%20consumers%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20they%20missed%20their%20health%20clubs%20as%20much%20as%20their%20friends%20and%20family%20during%20lockdowns.%20And%20in%20a%202023%20survey%20by%20Les%20Mills%2C%20two-thirds%20of%20Gen%20Zers%20said%20the%20social%20aspect%20was%20something%20they%20looked%20for%20in%20a%20gym.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20rarely%20go%20to%20the%20gym%20alone%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20Bhasin%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20always%20either%20meeting%20other%20people%20there%20or%20going%20with%20other%20people.%26quot%3B%20Where%20she%20lives%20in%20Portland%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20find%20places%20to%20hang%20out%20with%20friends.%20%26quot%3BYou%20go%20to%20a%20coffee%20shop%2C%20and%20even%20if%20you%20spend%20%248%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20sign%20there%20that%20says%20the%20maximum%20amount%20of%20time%20you%20can%20stay%20is%20two%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20me.%20Restaurants%20in%20her%20area%20also%20close%20early%20in%20the%20winter.%20%26quot%3BMy%20gym%20is%20open%2024%20hours%2C%20so%20we%20don't%20feel%20that%20pressure%20to%20have%20to%20leave.%26quot%3B%20She%20and%20her%20friends%20will%20hang%20out%20and%20catch%20up%20after%20their%20workouts%20or%20use%20the%20gym%20as%20a%20meeting%20place%20before%20heading%20to%20other%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20gyms%20are%20responding%20to%20the%20demand%20by%20redesigning%20spaces%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Floneliness-epidemic-decline-in-third-places-friends-parks-community-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebetter%20hangout%20spots%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BGyms%20have%20noticed%20that%20members%20also%20want%20a%20social%20aspect%20to%20the%20gym%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Renel%20Scarlett%2C%20a%20co-owner%20of%20The%20Works%20Health%20Club%2C%20an%20independent%20gym%20that%20focuses%20on%20building%20community%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhether%20that's%20running%20clubs%2C%20a%20coffee%20or%20refuel%20bar%20area%20where%20you%20can%20sit%20down%20and%20have%20a%20chat%20before%20class%20or%20after%20they%20train.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELife%20Time%2C%20a%20national%20health-club%20chain%2C%20has%20leaned%20into%20this%20model%20in%20recent%20years.%20When%20its%20membership%20dropped%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20it%20pivoted%20its%20business%20model%20to%20prioritize%20luxury%20social%20amenities%20like%20coworking%20spaces%20and%20pickleball%20courts%2C%20charging%20members%20more%20for%20them.%20The%20chain%20has%20added%20about%2065%2C000%20new%20members%20since%202021%2C%20and%20in%202023%20it%20grew%20its%20revenue%20by%20more%20than%2020%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20ways%2C%20it's%20a%20return%20to%20form.%20Fitness%20and%20socializing%20have%20long%20been%20combined.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-dont-like-country-clubs-membership-dues-evolution-2019-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECountry%20clubs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whose%20original%20facilities%20included%20tennis%20courts%2C%20polo%20fields%2C%20racetracks%2C%20and%20baseball%20diamonds%2C%20were%20an%20important%20part%20of%20the%20American%20social%20scene%20in%20the%2020th%20century.%20And%20local%20sports%20leagues%20and%20clubs%20have%20long%20filled%20the%20gaps%20left%20by%20the%20decline%20in%20other%20kinds%20of%20social%20groups.%20The%20only%20hang-up%20is%20that%20some%20gyms%20aren't%20prepared%20for%20the%20influx%20of%20patrons.%20In%20fact%2C%20many%20gyms%20actually%20depend%20on%20their%20members%20%3Cem%3Enot%3C%2Fem%3E%20showing%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplanet-fitness-ceo-chris-rondeau-cash-keg-alcohol-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPlanet%20Fitness%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20most%20popular%20gym%20franchise%20in%20the%20US%2C%20has%20on%20average%206%2C500%20members%20per%20gym.%20But%20most%20of%20its%20gyms%20hold%20only%20about%20300%20people.%20In%202022%2C%20it%20told%20CNN%20that%2060%25%20of%20its%20members%20didn't%20visit%20the%20gym%20in%20a%2030-day%20stretch.%20But%20they%20keep%20paying%20%E2%80%94%20the%20low%20monthly%20rate%20doesn't%20incentivize%20people%20to%20cancel%2C%20so%20the%20non-attendees%20subsidize%20the%20cost%20for%20those%20who%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20model%20is%20being%20stretched%20to%20its%20limit.%20Amelie%20Desai%2C%20a%20fitness%20and%20lifestyle%20influencer%20in%20California%2C%20attends%20her%20local%20gym%20up%20to%20six%20times%20a%20week.%20%26quot%3BOver%20the%20past%20three%20years%20I've%20noticed%20a%20significant%20increase%2C%20especially%20in%20young%20people%2C%20going%20to%20the%20gym%2C%26quot%3B%20Desai%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BThe%20weight%20section%20and%20the%20treadmills%20are%20always%20very%20busy%2C%20whereas%20the%20other%20random%20machines%2C%20like%20the%20bicycles%2C%20no%20one's%20ever%20on%20those%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScarlett%2C%20the%20Works%20Health%20Club%20co-owner%2C%20said%20most%20gyms%20he%20knows%20are%20increasing%20their%20weight%20areas%20because%20of%20demand.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20every%20five%20to%2010%20years%2C%20depending%20on%20what's%20trending%2C%20gyms%20will%20switch%20up%20the%20management%20layout%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20with%20a%20new%20layout%2C%20the%20low-cost%2C%20high-value%20gym%20model%20doesn't%20work%20when%20too%20many%20people%20start%20regularly%20attending%20the%20gym.%20Can%20you%20imagine%20if%206%2C500%20people%20tried%20to%20show%20up%20at%20one%20Planet%20Fitness%20location%20all%20at%20once%3F%20Taylor%20got%20so%20frustrated%20at%20how%20crowded%20her%20last%20gym%20was%20that%20she%20ditched%20it%20for%20one%20with%20more%20space.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20be%20waiting%20for%20the%20barbell%20for%2030%20minutes%20and%20just%20wasting%20my%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20report%20from%20the%20Health%20%26amp%3B%20Fitness%20Association%20said%20gyms%20with%20membership%20bases%20that%20exceeded%20their%20optimal%20capacity%20saw%20a%2020%25%20drop%20in%20member%20satisfaction%20from%202022%20to%202023.%20%26quot%3BThe%20churn%20rate%20for%20low-cost%20gyms%20can%20be%20as%20high%20as%2040%25%20annually%2C%26quot%3B%20Bassem%20Mostafa%2C%20a%20lead%20market%20analyst%20covering%20the%20gym%20and%20fitness%20industry%20and%20the%20owner%20of%20GlobeMonitor%20Market%20Research%20Agency%2C%20told%20me%2C%20citing%20his%20company's%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20the%20math%20just%20doesn't%20add%20up.%20It%20could%20be%20why%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplanet-fitness-membership-fee-classic-card-15-26-years-inflation-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPlanet%20Fitness%20is%20raising%20its%20price%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20nearly%2030%20years.%20This%20summer%2C%20the%20chain%20bumped%20up%20its%20rate%20to%20%2415%20a%20month%20from%20%2410%20after%20it%20reported%20weaker-than-expected%20first-quarter%20revenue.%20Gen%20Z's%20love%20of%20the%20gym%20might%20just%20drive%20more%20gyms%20to%20rethink%20their%20business%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20generation%2C%20the%20gym%20isn't%20just%20a%20place%20to%20simply%20shed%20a%20few%20pounds%3B%20it's%20a%20hub%20for%20improving%20their%20mental%20health%2C%20physical%20strength%2C%20and%20social%20connections.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20about%20how%20you%20look%2C%26quot%3B%20Desai%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20about%20how%20you%20feel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20it's%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeloton-earnings-stock-price-problems-ceo-leaves-layoffs-fitness-fads-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efitness%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20catch%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C