e%20first%20Indian%20woman%20to%20compete%20in%20the%20100m%20hurdles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Khushi%20Arora%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Akhilesh%20Yadav%20Alleges%20Speaker's%20Power%20Being%20Slashed%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20Responds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESamajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20today%20alleged%20that%20the%20rights%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20are%20being%20slashed%20and%20the%20Opposition%20would%20have%20to%20fight%20for%20him%2C%20drawing%20a%20sharp%20response%20from%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kannauj%20MP%20was%20addressing%20Lok%20Sabha%20during%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20Waqf%20(Amendment)%20Bill%20when%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYour%20rights%20and%20our%20rights%20are%20being%20curtailed.%20I%20had%20told%20you%20that%20you%20are%20the%20judge%20of%20democracy.%20I%20have%20heard%20that%20some%20of%20your%20rights%20are%20being%20snatched%20and%20we%20would%20have%20to%20fight%20for%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20rose%20to%20respond%20to%20Mr%20Yadav.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20insult%20of%20the%20Chair.%20The%20rights%20of%20the%20Speaker%20do%20not%20belong%20to%20the%20Opposition%2C%20but%20to%20the%20whole%20House.%20Don't%20speak%20in%20a%20roundabout%20way.%20You%20are%20not%20the%20protector%20of%20the%20Speaker's%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Birla%20later%20told%20Mr%20Yadav%20that%20he%20and%20other%20members%20of%20the%20House%20must%20not%20comment%20on%20the%20Chair.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20my%20expectation%2C%20no%20personal%20remarks%20should%20be%20made%20on%20the%20Chair%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposing%20the%20legislation%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%20it%20has%20been%20introduced%20as%20part%20of%20a%20well-thought-out%20politics.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20there%20is%20a%20democratic%20process%20for%20election%2C%20why%20nominate%20people%3F%20No%20person%20from%20outside%20the%20community%20is%20part%20of%20other%20religious%20bodies.%20What%20is%20the%20point%20of%20including%20non-Muslims%20in%20Waqf%20bodies%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20said%20the%20BJP%20has%20brought%20this%20legislation%20to%20appease%20some%20hardline%20supporters%20after%20its%20setback%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%20joined%20forces%20to%20oppose%20the%20legislation%20that%20aims%20to%20address%20issues%20related%20to%20powers%20of%20State%20Waqf%20Boards%2C%20registration%20and%20survey%20of%20Waqf%20properties%20and%20removal%20of%20encroachment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legislation%20proposes%20to%20amend%2044%20sections%20of%20the%201995%20Waqf%20Act.%20The%20Bill%20proposes%20that%20the%20Central%20Waqf%20Council%20and%20state%20Waqf%20Boards%20must%20have%20two%20women.%20It%20also%20lays%20down%20that%20money%20received%20by%20the%20Waqf%20Board%20must%20be%20used%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20widows%2C%20divorcees%2C%20and%20orphans%20in%20the%20manner%20suggested%20by%20the%20government.%20Another%20key%20proposal%20is%20that%20women's%20inheritances%20must%20be%20protected.%20The%20provision%20for%20including%20non-Muslim%20members%20of%20Waqf%20bodies%20is%20another%20contentious%20point%20in%20the%20proposed%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723108440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F5efqrfdo_akhilesh-yadav-_625x300_08_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fakhilesh-yadav-amit-shah-parliament-live-akhilesh-yadav-alleges-speakers-power-being-slashed-amit-shah-responds-6291373%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20today%20alleged%20that%20rights%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20are%20being%20slashed%20and%20the%20Opposition%20would%20have%20to%20fight%20