%20three%20young%20girls%20has%20spiralled%20into%20nationwide%20chaos%2C%20with%20far-right%20groups%20using%20the%20moment%20to%20incite%20anti-immigration%20and%20anti-Muslim%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20triggered%20the%20protests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2029%2C%20three%20young%20girls%2C%20aged%20six%20to%20nine%2C%20were%20killed%20during%20a%20Taylor%20Swift-themed%20dance%20event%20in%20Southport%2C%20northern%20England.%20Eight%20other%20children%20and%20two%20adults%20also%20suffered%20stab%20wounds%20and%20were%20transferred%20to%20the%20hospital.%20The%20attacker%2C%2017-year-old%20Axel%20Rudakubana%2C%20was%20arrested%20and%20charged%20with%20three%20counts%20of%20murder%2C%2010%20counts%20of%20attempted%20murder%20and%20one%20of%20possession%20of%20a%20blade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAxel%20Rudakubana%20was%20born%20and%20raised%20in%20Cardiff%2C%20Wales.%20However%2C%20false%20information%20that%20he%20was%20an%20Islamist%20migrant%20quickly%20spread%20on%20social%20media.%20This%20misinformation%20incited%20violent%20anti-Muslim%20protests%20in%20Southport%20the%20following%20day%2C%20including%20an%20attempted%20attack%20on%20the%20local%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpread%20of%20the%20riots%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%20evening%2C%20a%20sea%20of%20angry%20demonstrators%20descended%20upon%20Prime%20Minister%20Keir%20Starmer's%20Downing%20Street%20office%2C%20voicing%20their%20outrage%20over%20immigration%20and%20demanding%20action%20from%20the%20government.%20The%20crowd's%20chants%20of%20%26quot%3BSave%20our%20kids%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20our%20country%20back%26quot%3B%20filled%20the%20air%20as%20protesters%20clashed%20with%20police%2C%20hurling%20flares%20and%20smoke%20canisters%20towards%20the%20prime%20minister's%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Metropolitan%20police%20reported%20111%20arrests%20and%20five%20injured%20officers%2C%20following%20a%20night%20of%20violent%20disorder.%20This%20comes%20after%20Tuesday's%20initial%20protests%20in%20Southport%2C%20where%20over%2050%20police%20officers%20were%20hurt%20and%20police%20vans%20were%20set%20ablaze.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20riots%20have%20erupted%20in%20over%2020%20locations%2C%20including%20Sunderland%2C%20Manchester%2C%20Plymouth%20and%20Belfast%2C%20across%20Britain.%20These%20protests%20have%20involved%20hundreds%20of%20participants%20targeting%20migrants%20or%20Muslims%2C%20vandalising%20shops%2C%20and%20clashing%20with%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20behind%20the%20riots%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeir%20Starmer%20blames%20the%20recent%20violence%20on%20%26quot%3Bfar-right%20thuggery%26quot%3B.%20Prominent%20anti-Muslim%20and%20anti-immigration%20activists%2C%20like%20Stephen%20Yaxley-Lennon%2C%20are%20accused%20of%20spreading%20false%20information%20to%20inflame%20tensions.%20Social%20media%20platforms%20have%20been%20criticised%20for%20not%20preventing%20the%20spread%20of%20disinformation%2C%20which%20has%20played%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20amplifying%20these%20false%20narratives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20clashes%20were%20far-right%20agitators%20from%20outside%20the%20local%20areas.%20However%2C%20some%20individuals%20with%20local%20grievances%20or%20young%20people%20seeking%20excitement%20also%20joined%20the%20fray%2C%20police%20said.%20Meanwhile%2C%20counter-protesters%20and%20anti-fascist%20groups%20have%20gathered%20to%20oppose%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20motivation%20behind%20the%20riots%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20rioters%2C%20describing%20themselves%20as%20%26quot%3Bpatriots%26quot%3B%2C%20claimed%20that%20high%20immigration%20levels%20were%20undermining%20British%20society.%20They%20argued%20that%20immigration%20fueled%20violence%20and%20crime%20and%20that%20politicians%20favoured%20migrants.%20However%2C%20rights%20groups%20and%20anti-racist%20organisations%20rejected%20these%20claims%20as%20baseless%2C%20suggesting%20the%20true%20motive%20was%20extremism%20masked%20as%20patriotism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGovernment's%20response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Starmer-led%20government%20has%20taken%20swift%20action%20in%20response%20to%20the%20recent%20riots%2C%20making%20nearly%20600%20additional%20prison%20places%20available%20and%20deploying%20specialist%20officers%20to%20prevent%20the%20situation%20from%20spiralling.%20A%2058-year-old%20British%20man%20has%20also%20been%20jailed%20for%20three%20years%20for%20violent%20disorder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20is%20also%20targeting%20those%20using%20social%20media%20to%20spread%20trouble%2C%20with%20one%20man%20charged%20for%20using%20threatening%20language%20to%20stir%20up%20racial%20hatred%20on%20Facebook.%20Science%20Minister%20Peter%20Kyle%20has%20met%20with%20representatives%20from%20major%20tech%20companies%2C%20like%20TikTok%2C%20Meta%2C%20Google%20and%20X%2C%20to%20prevent%20incitement%20and%20the%20spread%20of%20false%20information%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723105740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fc973pnao_anti-racism-protests-uk-x-_625x300_08_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplained-why-are-there-anti-racism-protests-riots-in-the-uk-6289614%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20wave%20of%20riots%2C%20sparked%20by%20a%20deadly%20attack%20at%20a%20children's%20dance%20event%20and%20further%20fueled%20by%20a%20torrent%20of%20misinformation%2C%20has%20gripped%20parts%20of%20the%20United%20Kingdom.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplained-why-are-there-anti-racism-protests-riots-in-the-uk-6289614%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2