n%20others%2C%20some%20defeats%20more%20bitter%2C%20whatever%20the%20arena%20be.%20But%20what%20about%20the%20cruelty%20of%20fate%3F%20How%20does%20one%20take%20heart%3F%20The%20vagaries%20of%20destiny%20are%20more%20ruthless%20than%20any%20opponent's%20blow.%20They%20also%20feel%20more%20personal%2C%20as%20if%20the%20player%20in%20the%20arena%20is%20an%20alter%20ego%20of%20any%20and%20all%20of%20the%20spectators%20near%20and%20far.%20Vinesh%20Phogat's%20Paris%20Olympics%20performance%20is%20one%20such%20instance%20of%20the%20blurring%20of%20these%20boundaries.%20Many%20of%20her%20cheerleaders%20today%2C%20however%2C%20ought%20to%20be%20ashamed%20of%20themselves.%20Whether%20they%20will%20be%20is%20anyone's%20guess.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhogat%20has%20announced%20her%20retirement%20after%20being%20disqualified%20in%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%20just%20before%20her%20final%20bout.%20In%20Book%2022%20of%20the%20Iliad%2C%20Zeus-the%20king%20of%20gods-weighs%20the%20fates%20of%20Achilles%20and%20Hector%20before%20their%20first%20and%20final%20fight.%20Just%20like%20the%20scales%20dipped%20for%20Hector%2C%20foretelling%20his%20death%2C%20they%20foretold%20the%20death%20of%20Phogat's%20career.%20The%20past%2C%20present%2C%20and%20future%20of%20her%20sporting%20career%20weighed%20lighter%20than%20the%20weight%20mandates%20of%20her%20category.%20Her%20fate%2C%20quite%20literally%2C%20was%20decided%20by%20the%20wanton%20scales.%20This%20is%20a%20tragedy%20of%20epic%20proportions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20Was%20More%20Than%20Just%20A%20Medal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20a%20medal%20that%20Phogat%20lost%3B%20she%20lost%20something%20a%20lot%20more%20precious.%20Closure.%20Dragged%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20demeaned%2C%20and%20derided%20during%20the%20athletes'%20protest%20against%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20Phogat%20resolved%20to%20avenge%20her%20honour%20and%20that%20of%20many%20women%20athletes.%20She%20may%20have%20still%20achieved%20a%20watered-down%20form%20of%20vindication%2C%20but%20the%20optics%20are%20missing.%20In%20a%20spectacle-crazed%20nation%2C%20visual%20redemption%20is%20the%20only%20redemption.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sports%20culture%20of%20India%20can%20be%20defined%20by%20a%20peculiar%20tendency%20to%20delink%20the%20sport%20from%20the%20sportsperson.%20We%2C%20often%20lose%20the%20common-sense%20understanding%20that%20sportspersons%20are%20humans%20with%20all%20their%20foibles%20and%20frailties.%20We%20deify%20them%20with%20each%20victory%20and%20demonise%20them%20should%20they%20do%20anything%20but%20win%20medals.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20women%20athletes%2C%20this%20treatment%20is%20starkly%20naked%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20good%20old%20patriarchy.%20Men%20just%20have%20to%20be%20born%20while%20women%20have%20to%20be%20Olympic%20champions%2C%20along%20with%20everything%20else%2C%20to%20even%20claim%20parity.%20And%20even%20then%20it%20is%20denied%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20women%20are%20growing%20tired.%20One%20day%2C%20they%20might%20just%20give%20up.%20Many%20have.%20Simon%20Biles%20did.%20Sakshi%20Malik%20did.%20Naomi%20Osaka%20did.%20They%20tell%20themselves%20that%20enough%20is%20enough%3B%20they%20need%20not%20prove%20themselves%20yet%20again.%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20is%20not%20one%20of%20them.%20She%20knew%20she%20had%20to%20get%20on%20the%20Olympic%20podium%20to%20get%20her%20countrymen%20to%20listen%20to%20her.%20This%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20her%20soapbox.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Exactly%20Is%20A%20'Woman'%20In%20Sports%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20athletes%20are%20doubly%20disadvantaged%2C%20for%20they%20choose%20an%20arena%20that%20essentially%20devalues%20feminine%20attributes%20of%20their%20constitution.%20Athleticism%20is%20ostensibly%20partial%20to%20masculinity.%20Sports%20may%20give%20the%20impression%20of%20blurring%20gender%20boundaries%2C%20but%20the%20reality%20is%20the%20opposite.%20In%20the%20sporting%20arena%2C%20gendered%20attitudes%20are%20not%20only%20underscored%20but%20also%20magnified.%20Women%20are%20celebrated%20for%20exhibiting%20masculinity-not%20too%20much%20of%20it%2C%20though%2C%20lest%20they%20be%20accused%20of%20being%20a%20'man'.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDebates%20on%20gender%20bias%20in%20every%20sport%20in%20terms%20of%20legitimacy%2C%20pay%2C%20attention%2C%20etc%2C%20are%20so%20old%20and%20repetitive%20that%20even%20the%20staunchest%20of%20equality%20advocates%20are%20getting%20jaded.%20The%20more%20things%20change%2C%20the%20more%20they%20stay%20the%20same.%20This%20is%20particularly%20true%20of%20India%2C%20which%20also%20has%20a%20peculiar%20problem%20of%20one%20sport%20cannibalising%20every%20other.%20Women%20athletes%20in%20India%2C%20therefore%2C%20are%20heroes%20who%20must%20punch%20way%20above%20their%20weight%20every%20single%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhogat%20will%20soon%20be%20forgotten.%20She%20won't%20appear%20on%20India's%20list%20of%20Olympic%20medallists'%20and%20nobody%20will%20care%20for%20what%20she%20went%20through%20before%20she%20fought%20her%20way%20to%20the%20finals%20of%202024%20Olympics.%20Spectacles%2C%20as%20stated%20earlier%2C%20are%20important%20to%20engage%20fickle%20collective%20memory.%20The%20hurt%20and%20the%20heartbreak%20underscoring%20her%20retirement%20announcement%20ought%20to%20rekindle%20the%20fire%20in%20each%20woman%20athlete's%20belly%20in%20India.%20It%20should%20remind%20them%20that%20they%20are%2C%20after%20all%2C%20on%20their%20own.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETriple%20Measures%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESylvia%20Burrow%20proposes%20that%20%26quot%3Bimpaired%20live%20options%20for%20participating%20and%20succeeding%20in%20sport%20undermine%20women's%20autonomy%26quot%3B.%20Professional%20women%20athletes%20have%20to%20overcome%20that%20before%20taking%20their%20first%20step.%20When%20women%20enter%20competitive%20public%20spaces%2C%20they%20are%20already%20exhausted%20by%20all%20the%20behind-the-scenes%20fighting.%20Their%20opponents%20are%20not%20just%20in%20front%20of%20them%20but%20behind%20and%20alongside%20them.%20Each%20win%2C%20therefore%2C%20requires%20everything%20in%20triple%20measure%3A%20strength%2C%20resilience%2C%20will%2C%20and%20resources.%20Indian%20establishment%20and%20the%20public%20have%20been%20failing%20athletes%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20Women%20athletes%20in%20particular.%20Any%20show%20of%20support%20is%20but%20a%20blip%20on%20the%20radar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20the%20darned%20woman%20athlete%20takes%20our%20breath%20away.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Nishtha%20Gautam%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20author%20and%20academic.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723105560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fd7nhu89_vinesh_625x300_08_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fvinesh-phogat-the-darned-woman-athlete-taking-our-breath-away-6290880%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Phogat%20will%20soon%20be%20forgotten.%20She%20won't%20appear%20on%20India's%20list%20of%20Olympic%20medallists'%20and%20nobody%20will%20care%20for%20what%20she%20went%20through.%20Spectacles%2C%20as%20stated%20earlier%2C%20are%20important%20to%20engage%20fickle%20collective%20memory.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fvinesh-phogat-the-darned-woman-athlete-taking-our-breath-away-6290880%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Yunus%20lands%20in%20Bangladesh%20to%20lead%20caretaker%20government%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723105303000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F0f2c%2Flive%2F60f697b0-1203-11ef-82e8-cd354766a224.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%