point%20there%20were%20comments%20from%20the%20Chair's%20left%2C%20after%20which%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20pointed%20to%20Jairam%20Ramesh.%20%26quot%3BNow%20I%20have%20only%20option...%20after%20what%20I%20have%20seen%20today%2C%20for%20sometime%20I%20am%20not%20finding%20myself%20in%20a%20position%20to%20sit%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20after%20which%20he%20stood%20up%2C%20folded%20his%20hands%20together%2C%20and%20walked%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20circulated%20by%20BJP%20leader%20Satya%20Kumar%20Yadav%20showed%20a%20nearly-empty%20House%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EShameful%20behavior%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40Jairam_Ramesh%3C%2Fa%3E%20led%20to%20Dhankhar%20Sahib%20ji%20leaving%20the%20chair!%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnCongress%20leaders%20lack%20even%20basic%20decency%20in%20Parliament%20and%20then%20they%20have%20the%20audacity%20to%20blame%20others.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FwWyF1mcrie%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FwWyF1mcrie%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Satya%20Kumar%20Yadav%20(%40satyakumar_y)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsatyakumar_y%2Fstatus%2F1821442439720099980%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%208%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20absence%C2%A0Deputy%20Chairman%20Harivansh%20Narayan%20Singh%20chaired%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20afterwards%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20returned%20and%20hit%20out%20at%20%26quot%3Bunprecedented%2C%20indigestible%26quot%3B%20scenes%20in%20the%20House.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20our%20bounden%20duty%20to%20take%20tough%20decisions%20(but)%20sublimity%20has%20been%20misunderstood%20as%20fragility%2C%20persuasion%20as%20weakness%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dhankhar%20also%20said%20he%20had%2