%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Where%20Will%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20Go%3F%20Bangladesh%20Ex-PM's%20Options%20After%20Dhaka%20Exit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20back%2C%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20resigned%20as%20Bangladesh%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20fled%20capital%20Dhaka%20amid%20violent%20protests%20demanding%20her%20ouster%20and%20landed%20near%20Delhi.%20Since%20then%2C%20there%20has%20been%20speculation%20on%20where%20she%20is%20headed%20next.%20Right%20after%20her%20escape%20from%20Dhaka%2C%20some%20reports%20had%20claimed%20that%20the%2076-year-old%20leader%20plans%20to%20seek%20asylum%20in%20the%20UK.%20But%20with%20London%20hesitating%2C%20the%20Awami%20League%20leader%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20is%20looking%20at%20other%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20Son%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20son%20and%20Awami%20League%20leader%20Sajeeb%20Wazed%20Joy%20said%20reports%20claiming%20that%20his%20mother%20sought%20asylum%20in%20the%20UK%20are%20incorrect.%20%26quot%3BShe%20has%20not%20requested%20asylum%20anywhere%2C%20so%20the%20question%20of%20the%20UK%20or%20US%20not%20responding%20yet%20is%20not%20true.%20My%20mother%20was%20planning%20to%20retire%20after%20this%20term%20anyway.%20She%20is%20done%20with%20politics%20in%20Bangladesh.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Hasina's%20daughter%20Saima%20Wazed%20is%20WHO's%20Regional%20Director%20for%20South-East%20Asia%20and%20lives%20in%20Delhi.%20But%20a%20Twitter%20post%20she%20put%20up%20suggests%20that%20she%20has%20not%20met%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20after%20her%20escape%20from%20Dhaka.%20%26quot%3BHeartbroken%20with%20the%20loss%20of%20life%20in%20my%20country%20that%20I%20love.%20So%20heartbroken%20that%20I%20cannot%20see%20and%20hug%20my%20mother%20during%20this%20difficult%20time.%20I%20remain%20committed%20to%20my%20role%20as%20RD%20%40WHOSEARO%40WHO%23HealthForAll%23OneWHO%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Has%20UK%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Hasina's%20sister%20Sheikh%20Rehana%20is%20a%20UK%20citizen%2C%20and%20Rehana's%20daughter%20Tulip%20Siddiq%20is%20a%20Labour%20Party%20politician%20and%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Keir%20Starmer%20government.%20Also%2C%20the%20UK%20has%20a%20record%20of%20giving%20refuge%20to%20several%20prominent%20figures%20of%20the%20subcontinent%2C%20including%20former%20Pakistan%20president%20Pervez%20Musharraf%20and%20former%20Pakistan%20Prime%20Minister%20Nawaz%20Sharif.%20So%20soon%20after%20she%20fled%20Dhaka%2C%20multiple%20reports%20predicted%20that%20she%20is%20headed%20to%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20UK%20Home%20Office%20told%20NDTV%20that%20British%20immigration%20rules%20do%20not%20allow%20individuals%20to%20travel%20to%20that%20country%20to%20seek%20asylum%20or%20temporary%20refuge.%20A%20spokesperson%20also%20said%20individuals%20seeking%20asylum%20must%20do%20so%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20first%20safe%20country%20they%20reach%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20UK%20has%20a%20proud%20record%20of%20providing%20protection%20for%20people%20who%20need%20it.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20no%20provision%20for%20someone%20to%20be%20allowed%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20UK%20to%20seek%20asylum%20or%20temporary%20refuge%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Home%20office%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20US%20An%20Option%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Hasina's%20son%20Joy%20is%20based%20in%20the%20US%2C%20but%20the%20chances%20of%20her%20moving%20there%20are%20slim%20after%20Washington%20DC%20and%20Dhaka's%20ties%20nosedived%20during%20her%20tenure.%20In%20fact%2C%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20when%20Awami%20League%20stormed%20to%20victory%20in%20the%20Bangladesh%20election%2C%20the%20US%20State%20Department%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20United%20States%20remains%20concerned%20by%20the%20arrests%20of%20thousands%20of%20political%20opposition%20members%20and%20by%20reports%20of%20irregularities%20on%20elections%20day.%20The%20United%20States%20shares%20the%20view%20with%20other%20observers%20that%20these%20elections%20were%20not%20free%20or%20fair%20and%20we%20regret%20that%20not%20all%20parties%20participated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20reports%20say%20the%20US%20has%20cancelled%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20visa%20after%20she%20resigned%20as%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20official%20confirmation%20and%20authorities%20have%20said%20visa%20records%20are%20confidential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20after%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20fled%20the%20country%2C%20the%20US%20had%20said%20it%20stands%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Bangladesh.%20%26quot%3BWe%20welcome%20the%20announcement%20of%20an%20interim%20government%20and%20urge%20any%20transition%20be%20conducted%20in%20accordance%20with%20Bangladesh's%20laws%2C%26quot%3B%20State%20Department%20spokesperson%20Matthew%20Miller%20had%20said%2C%20flagging%20reports%20of%20human%20rights%20abuses%2C%20casualties%2C%20and%20injuries%20during%20the%20violent%20protests%20against%20the%20Awami%20League%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20About%20India%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Hasina%20has%20been%20in%20India%20since%20she%20landed%20here%20Monday.%20Addressing%20the%20Parliament%20on%20the%20Bangladesh%20situation%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20had%20sought%20approval%20to%20come%20to%20India%20on%20a%20very%20short%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20according%20to%20reports%2C%20has%20told%20an%20all-party%20meeting%20that%20they%20have%20given%20time%20to%20the%20veteran%20politician%20to%20decide%20on%20her%20next%20move.%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20is%20in%20a%20state%20of%20shock%20and%20the%20government%20is%20giving%20her%20time%20to%20recover%20before%20it%20discusses%20these%20issues%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%20also%20faces%20a%20diplomatic%20dilemma%20here.%20It%20does%20not%20want%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20overtly%20backing%20the%20ousted%20leader%20because%20that%20may%20complicate%20its%20relationship%20with%20the%20new%20dispensation%20in%20Bangladesh%2Ca%20a%20strategic%20partner%20geopolitically.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20history%20of%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20relationship%20with%20India%20must%20also%20be%20kept%20in%20mind.%20Long%20before%20she%20became%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20government%20had%20given%20her%20refuge%20after%20her%20whole%20family%2C%20including%20father%20Mujibur%20Rahaman%2C%20was%20assassinated%20during%20the%201975%20unrest%20in%20Bangladesh.%20So%20abandoning%20her%20at%20this%20point%20will%20also%20not%20be%20an%20easy%20decision%2C%20considering%20her%20equations%20with%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723103400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F6etffbkg_sheikh-hasina-afp_625x300_06_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsheikh-hasina-bangladesh-protests-where-will-sheikh-hasina-go-bangladesh-ex-pms-options-after-dhaka-exit-6290306%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20days%20back%2C%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20resigned%20as%20Bangladesh%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20fled%20capital%20Dhaka%20amid%20violent%20protests%20demanding%20her%20ouster%20and%20landed%20near%20Delhi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsheikh-hasina-bangladesh-protests-where-will-sheikh-hasina-go-bangladesh-ex-pms-options-after-dhaka-exit-6290306%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vinesh%20Phogat%20Row%20In%20Parliament%3A%20Opposition%20Demands%20Discussion%2C%20Walks%20Out%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20wrestler%20Vinesh%20Phogat's%20gut-wrenching%20disqualification%20from%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20her%20gold%20medal%20quest%2C%20Opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%20members%20demanded%20a%20discussion%20in%20parliament%20and%20staged%20a%20walkout%20today%20from%20Rajya%20Sabha%20when%20their%20demand%20was%20rejected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinesh%20Phogat%20was%20on%20Wednesday%20disqualified%20for%20being%20100%20grams%20overweight%2C%20hours%20before%20she%20was%20to%20take%20on%20the%20US'%20Sarah%20Ann%20Hildebrandt%20in%20the%20historic%2050-kg%20freestyle%20gold%20medal%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20day's%20business%20started%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20and%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20raised%20the%20disqualification%20of%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20and%20questioned%20%26quot%3Bwho%20is%20behind%20it%26quot%3B.%20Vice%20President%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20did%20not%20allow%20a%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Derek%20O'Brien%20also%20stood%20up%20to%20raise%20some%20issues%20but%20was%20not%20allowed%20by%20the%20Chair.%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20cautioned%20the%20Trinamool%20leader%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20shouting%20at%20the%20Chair.%20Your%20conduct%20is%20ugliest%20in%20the%20House.%20I%20condemn%20your%20actions.%20Next%20time%20I%20will%20show%20you%20the%20door.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20uproar%20escalated%2C%20Opposition%20leaders%20staged%20a%20walkout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dhankhar%20remarked%20that%20the%20Opposition%20believed%20they%20were%20the%20%26quot%3Bonly%20ones%20whose%20hearts%20are%20bleeding%26quot%3B%20after%20Ms%20Phogat's%20shocking%20exit%20from%20the%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20nation%20is%20in%20pain...%20But%20to%20politicise%20it%20is%20the%20greatest%20disrespect%20to%20her%20(Ms%20Phogat)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Opposition%20walks%20out%20from%20Rajya%20Sabha%20over%20the%20issue%20of%20Vinesh%20Phogat's%20disqualification%20from%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnRajya%20Sabha%20Chairman%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20says%2C%26quot%3B...They%20(Opposition)%20think%20they%20are%20the%20only%20ones%20whose%20hearts%20are%20bleeding...The%20entire%20nation%20is%20in%20pain%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FXTyrldhgla%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FXTyrldhgla%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1821430917912842349%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%208%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dhankhar%20also%20later%20walked%20out%20saying%20he%20did%20not%20get%20%26quot%3Bsupport%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20Wednesday%2C%20INDIA%20bloc%20members%20had%20walked%20out%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20after%20expressing%20their%20dissatisfaction%20with%20Union%20Sports%20Minister%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya's%20statement%20in%20on%20Ms%20Phogat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20opposition%20leaders%20hit%20out%20at%20Mr%20Mandaviya%20for%20detailing%20the%20financial%20assistance%20given%20to%20the%20grappler%20for%20her%20Olympics%20preps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESports%20Minister's%20Statement%20On%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20In%20Lok%20Sabha%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%20said%20the%20government%20had%20provided%20all%20possible%20assistance%20to%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20according%20to%20her%20requirements%2C%20which%20included%20personal%20staff.%20He%20said%20a%20total%20financial%20assistance%20of%20Rs%2070%2C45%2C775%20was%20given%20for%20the%20Paris%20Olympic%20cyc