3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETech%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk%20further%20stirred%20the%20situation%20by%20suggesting%20online%20that%20a%20civil%20war%20in%20Britain%20looked%20inevitable%20-%20a%20comment%20condemned%20heavily%20by%20the%20Labour%20government%20for%20being%20%26quot%3Birresponsible%26quot%3B%20and%20inciting%20violence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Led%20To%20The%20Protests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20a%20week%20ago%2C%20three%20girls%20under%20the%20age%20of%2010%20were%20brutally%20stabbed%20to%20death%20while%20attending%20a%20dance%20event%20in%20the%20peaceful%20coastal%20town%20of%20Stockport%2C%20near%20Liverpool.%20Ten%20others%20were%20wounded%20in%20the%20attack.%20A%2017-year-old%20boy%2C%20Axel%20Muganwa%20Rudakubana%2C%20was%20arrested%20and%20charged%20with%20murder.%20His%20identity%20was%20initially%20withheld%20due%20to%20legal%20reasons%20(under%20British%20law%2C%20suspects%20under%2018%20cannot%20be%20named)%20until%20a%20court%20in%20Liverpool%20allowed%20the%20media%20to%20disclose%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20then%2C%20however%2C%20violent%20protests%20had%20already%20spread%20across%20several%20towns%2C%20fuelled%20by%20social%20media%20rumours%20that%20the%20boy%20was%20Muslim%20and%20came%20to%20England%20%26quot%3Bby%20boat%26quot%3B%20in%202023%20-%20an%20implication%20that%20he%20was%20an%20illegal%20immigrant%20or%20an%20asylum%20seeker.%20No%20matter%20the%20fact%20that%20in%20reality%2C%20the%20boy%20is%20not%20Muslim%20and%20was%20born%20in%20Cardiff%20to%20Rwandan%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViolence%20has%20now%20spread%20to%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20towns%20and%20cities%20in%20Britain.%20Except%20for%20Belfast%2C%20all%20the%20affected%20cities%20are%20in%20England%2C%20mostly%20in%20the%20economically%20weaker%20north%2C%20where%20unemployment%20is%20higher%20than%20in%20the%20south.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Are%20the%20Rioters%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20prominent%20far-right%20figures%20have%20been%20actively%20posting%20messages%20on%20social%20media.%20Tommy%20Robinson%20(aka%20Stephen%20Yaxley-Lennon)%2C%20a%20well-known%20far-right%20and%20anti-Muslim%20activist%20who%20founded%20the%20now-defunct%20English%20Defence%20League%20(EDL)%20in%202009%2C%20has%20posted%20several%20videos%20online%20that%20have%20amassed%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20views%20and%20have%20been%20shared%20by%20right-wing%20outlets%20worldwide.%20A%20common%20anti-Muslim%20narrative%20with%20comments%20like%20%26quot%3Binnocent%20English%20people%20being%20hunted%20down%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bour%20women%20are%20not%20halal%20meat%26quot%3B%20marks%20Robinson's%20online%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20after%20the%20Southport%20attack%2C%20Robinson%20posted%20a%20video%20asking%20his%20followers%20to%20stay%20calm%2C%20asserting%20that%20he%20condemned%20the%20violence.%20But%20a%20few%20far-right%20popular%20figures%20had%20by%20then%20already%20started%20baying%20for%20violence%2C%20with%20tweets%20like%20%26quot%3Bit's%20war%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bfor%20decades%20British%20girls%20have%20been%20raped%20by%20immigrant%20barbarians%26quot%3B.%20These%20posts%20got%20over%20three%20million%20views%20in%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20said%20a%20vigil%20in%20Stockport%20was%20hijacked%20by%20right-wing%20extremists.%20They%20believe%20the%20protesters%20coordinated%20on%20WhatsApp%20and%20Telegram%20to%20organise%20protests%20in%20various%20towns%20and%20targeted%20mosques%2C%20shops%2C%20and%20hotels%20housing%20asylum%20seekers%2C%20especially%20in%20Rotherham%20and%20Tamworth.%20Starmer%20himself%20has%20termed%20the%20riots%20%26quot%3Bfar-right%20thuggery%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFar-Right%20Grievances%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20violence%20cannot%20be%20attributed%20solely%20to%20far-right%20inflammatory%20comments%20on%20social%20media.%20There%20is%20deep-rooted%20resentment%20in%20the%20country%20against%20immigration%2C%20particularly%20illegal%20immigration.%20The%20Stockport%20stabbings%20may%20have%20triggered%20these%20pent-up%20frustrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFar-right%20groups%20argue%20that%20the%20UK%20is%20experiencing%20uncontrolled%20immigration%2C%20which%20has%20overwhelmed%20public%20services%2C%20the%20housing%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20the%20welfare%20system.%20Nearly%20every%20day%2C%20small%20boats%20full%20of%20migrants%20cross%20the%20channel%20and%20enter%20the%20UK.%20The%20Tory%20government%20was%20unable%20to%20control%20this.%20According%20to%20the%20Home%20Office%20website%2C%20more%20than%20570%20migrants%20have%20arrived%20in%20the%20UK%20on%2011%20small%20boats%20since%20the%20protests%20erupted%20following%20the%20Stockport%20stabbings.%20These%20migrants%20seek%20asylum%20and%20are%20housed%20in%20hotels%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20protesters%20have%20links%20to%20far-right%20groups.%20Many%20resent%20that%20asylum%20seekers%20are%20given%20four-star%20hotels%20and%20money%20for%20their%20daily%20needs%2C%20while%20local%20youth%20struggle%20and%20live%20in%20poverty.%20Far-right%20activists%20often%20assert%20that%20immigrants%20take%20jobs%20from%20native%20Britons%20and%20undercut%20British%20workers%2C%20leading%20to%20unemployment%20and%20wage%20stagnation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMusk%20Jibe%20Against%20the%20UK%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20is%20not%20alone%20in%20criticising%20Britain.%20Donald%20Trump's%20running%20mate%2C%20J.D.%20Vance%2C%20went%20so%20far%20as%20to%20say%20that%20Britain%20would%20become%20an%20Islamist%20country.%20He%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20and%20I%20was%20talking%20about%2C%20you%20know%2C%20what%20is%20the%20first%20truly%20Islamist%20country%20that%20will%20get%20a%20nuclear%20weapon%2C%20and%20we%20were%20like%2C%20maybe%20it's%20Iran%2C%20you%20know%2C%20maybe%20Pakistan%20already%20kind%20of%20counts%2C%20and%20then%20we%20finally%20decided%20maybe%20it's%20actually%20the%20UK%2C%20since%20Labour%20just%20took%20over.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVance%20echoed%20the%20fears%20of%20far-right%20people%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20who%20believe%20Muslims%20in%20the%20country%20want%20to%20establish%20Sharia%20law.%20They%20loathe%20the%20perceived%20failure%20of%20immigrants%2C%20particularly%20Muslims%2C%20to%20integrate%20into%20British%20society.%20Far-right%20activists%20argue%20that%20this%20leads%20to%20the%20formation%20of%20isolated%20communities%20with%20different%20cultural%20norms%2C%20undermining%20British%20values%20and%20social%20cohesion.%20They%20fear%20that%20Britain%20is%20becoming%20an%20Islamic%20country%2C%20claiming%20that%20increasing%20Muslim%20populations%20threaten%20the%20traditional%20British%20way%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFar-right%20groups%20link%20immigration%2C%20especially%20illegal%20immigration%2C%20to%20increased%20crime%20and%20terrorism%2C%20suggesting%20that%20more%20immigrants%20from%20Muslim-majority%20countries%20increase%20the%20risk%20of%20terrorist%20attacks%20and%20crime%20rates.%20To%20support%20their%20claims%2C%20they%20cite%20examples%20like%20the%202005%20London%20terror%20attacks%20and%20British%20Muslim%20men%20and%20women%20joining%20jihadist%20movements%20in%20Iraq%20and%20Syria.%20These%20narratives%20are%20amplified%20through%20social%20media%20and%20far-right%20media%20outlets%2C%20which%20use%20inflammatory%20language%20to%20rally%20support%20and%20provoke%20strong%20emotional%20reactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFar-right%20activists%20also%20accuse%20the%20police%20of%20%26quot%3Btwo-tier%20policing%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20media%20of%20%26quot%3Btwo-tier%20coverage%26quot%3B%2C%20believing%20they%20are%20treated%20more%20harshly%20than%20other%20protesters%2C%20such%20as%20the%20recent%20pro-Gaza%20protesters.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Starmer%20government%20has%20not%20yet%20organised%20meetings%20between%20various%20groups%20or%20talked%20to%20the%20protesters.%20For%20example%2C%20during%20the%20Hindu-Muslim%20riots%20in%20Leicester%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20all-faith%20meetings%20were%20organised%20to%20stem%20the%20violence%20and%20instil%20confidence%20among%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20street%20violence%20continues%2C%20Keir%20Starmer's%20new%20government's%20honeymoon%20period%20is%20well%20and%20truly%20over.%20His%20month-old%20Prime%20Ministership%20will%20be%20judged%20on%20how%20he%20handles%20the%20ongoing%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Syed%20Zubair%20Ahmed%20is%20a%20London-based%20senior%20Indian%20journalist%20with%20three%20decades%20of%20experience%20with%20the%20Western%20media)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723098060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fgbig9r9g_uk_625x300_08_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbritain-on-the-boil-whats-behind-the-street-violence-sweeping-through-uk-6290112%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20street%20violence%20continues%2C%20Keir%20Starmer's%20new%20government's%20honeymoon%20period%20is%20well%20and%20truly%20over.%20His%20month-old%20Prime%20Ministership%20will%20be%20judged%20on%20how%20he%20handles%20the%20ongoing%20crisis.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbritain-on-the-boil-whats-behind-the-street-violence-sweeping-through-uk-6290112%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Black%20Panther%20actress%20Connie%20Chiume%20passes%20away%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723098056000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112366608%2Cimgsize-1451048.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesof