le-east%2Fisrael-vows-to-eliminate-new-hamas-chief-stokes-fears-of-deepening-gaza-war%2Famp_articleshow%2F112364831.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-vows-to-eliminate-new-hamas-chief-stokes-fears-of-deepening-gaza-war%2Famp_articleshow%2F112364831.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vinesh%20Phogat%20Could've%20Won%20Olympics%20Silver%2C%20Only%20If%20This%20Condition%20Was%20Met%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVinesh%20Phogat's%20unexpected%20disqualification%20from%20the%20Paris%20Olympic%20Games%20sent%20shockwaves%20across%20the%20Indian%20sporting%20spectrum.%20The%20authority's%20decision%20triggered%20a%20plethora%20of%20questions%20among%20fans%20on%20social%20media%2C%20as%20everyone%20wondered%20why%20Vinesh%20couldn't%20lose%20the%20last%20100%20grams%20to%20fall%20under%20the%2050kg%20mark%2C%20in%20order%20to%20compete%20in%20the%20gold%20medal%20match.%20Vinesh%20was%20competing%20in%20the%2050kg%20freestyle%20wrestling%20event%2C%20as%20the%2053kg%20category%20was%20blocked%20by%20fellow%20wrestler%20Antim%20Panghal.%20Vinesh%2C%20whose%20natural%20weight%20is%20around%2056-57kg%2C%20found%20it%20tough%20to%20manage%20her%20weight%2C%20which%20eventually%20became%20the%20reason%20behind%20her%20exit%20from%20the%20Paris%20Games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cstrong%3EMyth-buster%20guide%20to%20Vinesh%20Phogat's%20disqualification%20from%20the%20Paris%20Games%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWas%20Vinesh%20Overweight%20On%20Day%201%20of%20her%20events%20too%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20Vinesh%20wasn't%20overweight%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20events.%20She%20did%20the%20weigh-in%20before%20the%20bouts%20and%20had%20made%20the%20cut%20under%20the%2050kg%20mark.%20That's%20why%20she%20was%20allowed%20to%20compete.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20did%20Vinesh%20gain%20weight%20ahead%20of%20the%20Day%202%20of%20her%20events%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20her%20bouts%2C%20Vinesh%20had%20to%20drink%20water%20and%20eat%20basic%20food%20like%20fruits%2C%20vegetables%2C%20and%20some%20bread%20to%20replenish%20the%20lost%20energy.%20If%20anyone%20does%20that%2C%20the%20person%20can%20easily%20put%20on%202%20kilos%20of%20weight%2C%20especially%20when%20your%20body%20is%20drained%2C%20which%20Vinesh's%20was%20as%20she%20was%20competing%20in%20a%20weight%20category%20that%20didn't%20come%20naturally%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20couldn't%20Vinesh%20lose%20the%20desired%20weight%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20consuming%20some%20water%20and%20food%2C%20post%20her%20bouts%20on%20the%20first%20day%2C%20Vinesh%20had%20put%20on%20weight.%20She%20worked%20all%20night%20to%20meet%20the%2050kg%20criteria.%20She%20did%20manage%20to%20reach%20the%20mark%20of%2050kg%20and%20100%20grams%20but%20the%20last%20cut%20couldn't%20be%20made%20as%20she%20was%20incredibly%20deplted.%20She%20was%20so%20drained%20that%20sweat%20couldn't%20be%20induced%20and%20the%20weight%20reduction%20wasn't%20what%20she%20wanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECould%20Vinesh%20have%20been%20given%20an%20exception%2C%20since%20she%20was%20overweight%20by%20just%20100gms%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20the%20margin%20doesn't%20matter.%20It's%20a%20strict%20weight%20limit%20of%2050.00%20kilograms%2C%20even%20if%20she%20weighed%201%20milligram%20more%20than%20that%2C%20she%20would've%20been%20disqualified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWould%20Phogat%20have%20won%20a%20medal%20had%20she%20declared%20herself%20injured%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Vinesh%20declared%20herself%20injured%20on%20the%20second%20day%2C%20before%20the%20new%20weigh-in%2C%20then%20the%20UWW%20medical%20officer%20would%20have%20had%20to%20come%20in%20and%20check%20in%20on%20her.%20Even%20in%20this%20case%2C%20Vinesh%20would%20have%20had%20to%20give%20her%20weight%2C%20and%20if%20it%20exceeded%2C%20she%20would've%20been%20disqualified.%20The%20only%20way%20Vinesh%20could've%20retained%20her%20results%20and%20won%20a%20silver%20medal%20is%20if%20she%20had%20declared%20herself%20injured%20on%20the%20first%20day%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UWW%20rule%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20an%20athlete%20does%20not%20attend%20or%20fails%20the%20weigh-in%20(the%201st%20or%20the%202nd%20weigh-in)%2C%20he%20will%20be%20eliminated%20from%20the%20competition%20and%20ranked%20last%2C%20without%20rank.%20If%20an%20athlete%20is%20injured%20during%20the%20first%20day%2C%20he%20doesn't%20have%20to%20attend%20the%20second%20weigh-in%20and%20will%20keep%20his%20results.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Vinesh%20wasn't%20given%20a%20silver%20medal%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisqualification%20means%20the%20wrestler%20would%20not%20get%20any%20medal%2C%20and%20all%20her%20results%20in%20the%20event%20would%20be%20nullified.%20Hence%2C%20no%20silver%20medal%20for%20Vinesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECould%20Vinesh%20have%20been%20given%20extra%20time%20to%20reduce%20her%20weight%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20UWW%20rule%20that%20states%20that%20the%20weigh-in%20has%20to%20take%20place%20early%20in%20the%20morning.%20The%20intent%20is%20to%20give%20wrestlers%20enough%20time%20to%20replenish%20themselves%20before%20the%20bout%20and%20not%20go%20on%20the%20mat%2C%20depleted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20the%202-day%20weigh-in%20rule%20a%20new%20thing%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo.%20The%20rule%20was%20brought%20in%202017%2C%20when%20the%20UWW%20changed%20the%20format%20of%20Olympic%20wrestling%20from%20one%20day%20to%20two%20days.%20This%20decision%20was%20taken%20to%20help%20athletes%2C%20preventing%20them%20from%20losing%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20weight%20in%20one%20day%20and%20compete.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723094760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fq3lks15_vinesh-phogat-afp_