08%20months%20of%20relentless%20efforts%20for%20the%20police%20to%20actually%20file%20an%20FIR%2C%20says%20Dushyant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReddit%20is%20filled%20with%20appreciation%20posts%20for%20St%20Broseph%2C%20who%20goes%20above%20and%20beyond%20to%20help%20others%2C%20with%20people%20calling%20him%20Batman%20and%20thanking%20him%20for%20everything%20he%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitesh%2C%20a%20student%2C%20took%20Dushyant%E2%80%99s%20help%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20for%20a%20pervert%20who%20was%20flashing%20women%20in%20the%20neighbourhood.%20He%20was%20able%20to%20register%20a%20complaint%20and%20the%20case%20is%20in%20court%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBroseph%20helped%20us%20with%20all%20the%20details%20about%20filing%20a%20complaint%20and%20what%20evidence%20is%20needed.%20He%20was%20instrumental%20in%20these%20women%20seeking%20justice.%20His%20team%20followed%20up%20with%20us%20and%20helped%20us%20in%20every%20step.%20We%20have%20our%20own%20Batman%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Hitesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20would%20question%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%E2%80%99s%20in%20it%20for%20him%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20the%20right%20to%20work%20but%20never%20to%20its%20fruits.%20Let%20not%20the%20fruits%20of%20action%20be%20your%20motive%2C%20nor%20let%20your%20attachment%20be%20to%20inaction%2C%E2%80%9D%20is%20his%20mantra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20candidly%20accepts%20that%20while%20saying%20it%20is%20easy%2C%20there%20are%20difficult%20days.%20But%20knowing%20that%20this%20is%20the%20right%20path%20helps%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSocial%20workers%20should%20forgo%20the%20thought%20of%20any%20personal%20gain%20from%20their%20work.%20This%20work%20is%20strictly%20for%20society%2C%20and%20any%20kind%20of%20expectations%20will%20only%20serve%20to%20bring%20it%20down.%20The%20moment%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20expect%20anything%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20free%20yourself%20up%20to%20truly%20do%20everything.%20That