ways%20fascinated%20with%20javelin.%20Whenever%20I%20went%20to%20local%20meets%20I%20used%20to%20watch%20the%20event.%20Annu%20used%20to%20play%20cricket%20with%20us%20and%20had%20a%20strong%20arm.%20I%20asked%20her%20to%20try%20javelin%2C%E2%80%9D%20Upendra%20shared%20in%20an%20interview.%20So%20he%20began%20coaching%20Annu%20by%20having%20her%20throw%20sticks%20in%20an%20empty%20sugarcane%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20means%20to%20buy%20a%20javelin%2C%20Annu%20fashioned%20her%20own%20in%202010%20when%20she%20turned%2018.%20Whether%20she%20was%20tossing%20cricket%20balls%20or%20sugarcane%20sticks%2C%20these%20activities%20helped%20her%20build%20strong%20arms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20father%20Amarpal%E2%80%99s%20disapproval%20did%20not%20deter%20Annu%2C%20who%20was%20determined%20not%20to%20marry%20early%20like%20other%20girls%20in%20her%20village.%20In%20an%20interview%2C%20she%20revealed%20that%20she%20was%20forbidden%20from%20wearing%20T-shirts%20and%20playing%20sports.%20Financial%20constraints%20forced%20her%20to%20borrow%20jerseys%20and%20javelins%20from%20other%20players%20and%20make%20do%20with%20their%20oversized%20shoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhere%20I%20come%20from%2C%20girls%20are%20expected%20to%20depend%20on%20their%20parents%20and%20must%20always%20beg%20their%20father%20or%20brother%20for%20anything%20they%20need.%20After%20turning%2020%2C%20girls%20are%20often%20considered%20a%20burden%20and%20married%20off%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20expectation%20that%20women%20should%20constantly%20depend%20on%20men%2C%20both%20before%20and%20after%20marriage%2C%20disturbed%20Annu%20and%20made%20the%20world%20seem%20limited%20for%20women.%20She%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20accept%20the%20life%20expected%20of%20her%20and%20viewed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359674%2Flovlina-borgohain-paris-olympics-2024-indian-boxer-assam-first-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esports%20as%20her%20way%20out%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Without%20a%20clear%20path%20or%20training%20options%2C%20she%20chose%20javelin%20because%20it%20required%20just%20a%20sugarcane%20stick.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20father%20wanted%20to%20initially%20stick%20to%20local%20customs%20and%20marry%20her%20off.%20However%2C%20as%20the%20youngest%20sibling%2C%20she%20managed%20to%20persuade%20him%20to%20allow%20her%20to%20study%20until%20Class%2012%2C%20with%20support%20from%20her%20brothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20her%20training%20was%20confined%20to%20the%20farm%20fields%2C%20and%20she%20kept%20it%20discreet.%20She%20practised%20with%20sugarcane%20sticks%20after%20school.%20After%20a%20schoolboy%20reported%20her%20activities%20to%20her%20father%2C%20asking%2C%20%E2%80%9CDo%20you%20know%20your%20daughter%20is%20playing%20in%20the%20fields%3F%E2%80%9D%2C%20her%20father%2C%20surprised%2C%20went%20to%20the%20school%20to%20scold%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20teacher%20advised%20him%20to%20let%20Annu%20continue%20for%20a%20while.%20%E2%80%9CShe%E2%80%99ll%20stop%20when%20she%E2%80%99s%20had%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20teacher%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20her%20father%20began%20to%20show%20his%20support.%20He%20would%20cycle%2C%20with%20her%20running%20alongside%20him.%20To%20keep%20her%20training%20discreet%2C%20he%20scheduled%20her%20practice%20sessions%20before%20the%20villagers%20returned%20from%20work%20to%20avoid%20drawing%20their%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20new%20chapter%20began%20in%20Annu%E2%80%99s%20life%20after%20she%20clinched%20gold%20at%20the%202014%20National%20Inter-State%20Athletics%20Championship%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20breaking%20a%2014-year-old%20national%20record%20with%20a%2058.83m%20javelin%20throw.%20She%20qualified%20for%20the%20Commonwealth%20Games%2C%20where%20she%20finished%20eighth.%20Her%20father%2C%20now%20confident%20in%20her%20potential%2C%20encouraged%20her%20to%20continue%20with%20javelin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Annu%20achieved%20a%20personal%20best%20of%2063.82m%20at%20the%20Indian%20Open%20Javelin%20Throws%20Competition%20in%20Jamshedpur%2C%20setting%20a%20new%20national%20record%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20javelin%20throw%20in%20India.%20She%20also%20made%20history%20at%20the%202023%20Asian%20Games%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20to%20win%20gold%20in%20javelin%20with%20a%20throw%20of%2062.92m.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20prepares%20for%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%202024%2C%20Annu%E2%80%99s%20extraordinary%20rise%20from%20throwing%20sugarcane%20sticks%20to%20setting%20national%20records%20and%20winning%20gold%20medals%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F259922%2Fneeraj-chopra-javelin-tokyo-olympics-haryana-obesity-world-champion%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworld%20of%20javelin%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20story%20of%20unyielding%20spirit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20Annu%20Rani%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsY2DrGSvMD%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_copy_link%26igsh%3DMzRlODBiNWFlZA%3D%3D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%40annurani_%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sportskeeda.com%2Fsummer-olympics%2Fnews-who-annu-rani-all-need-know-indian-woman-javelin-thrower-competing-paris-2024-olympics%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWho%20is%20Annu%20Rani%3F%20All%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20the%20Indian%20woman%20javelin%20thrower%20competing%20at%20the%20Paris%202024%20Olympics%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%3A%2