%20Milk%20to%20Turn%20His%20Life%20Around%3B%20Earns%20Rs%2012%20Lakh%2FYear%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENearly%20two%20decades%20back%2C%20a%20few%20renowned%20officials%20of%20the%20agriculture%20department%20travelled%20in%20a%20convoy%20to%20Deh%20Kalan%20village%20in%20Sangrur%20district%20of%20Punjab.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20officials%20included%20Punjab%20Agriculture%20University%20(PAU)%20vice%20chancellor%20Dr%20GS%20Kallat%20and%20agriculture%20scientist%20Dr%20MS%20Swaminathan%2C%20popularly%20known%20as%20the%20Father%20of%20Green%20Revolution%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20their%20meeting%20at%20the%20deputy%20commissioner%E2%80%99s%20office%20that%20they%20came%20to%20know%20about%20Bachittar%20Singh%20Garcha%E2%80%99s%20soybean%20processing%20unit.%20Surprised%20at%20the%20novel%20initiative%20to%20process%20soybean%20in%20a%20region%20that%20was%20dominated%20by%20wheat%20and%20paddy%20cultivation%2C%20they%20strived%20to%20meet%20the%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20surprised%20to%20see%20so%20many%20officials%20outside%20my%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2065-year-old%20farmer%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20humble%20farmer%20offered%20them%20freshly-prepared%20tofu%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F173064%2Fmilk-cow-camel-almond-coconut-yak-goat-soy-coconut-alternative-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoy%20milk%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CDr%20Swaminathan%20ate%20paneer%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20had%20milk%20as%20well.%20He%20really%20liked%20the%20products%20and%20asked%20me%20where%20I%20marketed%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20jokingly%20revealed%20to%20the%20scientist%20that%20he%20just%20gives%20away%20the%20products%20for%20free%2C%20he%20was%20surprised.%20But%2C%20that%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20turning%20point%2C%20says%20Bachittar%2C%20as%20he%20never%20had%20to%20give%20away%20